NG0282:1907: dug gsum mchod pa bla na med //
NG0282:1909: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:1910: hum me yi rgyal po khro bo'i sku //
NG0282:1913: khams gsum 'khor ba gzhom pa dang *//
NG0282:1914: nyon mongs log lta bsreg pa'i phyir //
NG0282:1915: ye shes me chen 'bar ba yis //
NG0282:1916: 'khor ba'i bag chags bsreg pa dang *//
NG0282:1917: dngos grub 'tshe ba'i gdug pa can //
NG0282:1918: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i me la bsreg / rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:1919: rdzas sgrub pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ///
NG0282:1920: / de nas bcom ldan 'das rdzas thams cad bsgrub
NG0282:1921: par gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:1922: te // rdzas rnams bsgrubs nas rab tu bcangs //
NG0282:1923: gang la thob pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:1924: de ni 'grub par gdon mi za //
NG0282:1925: mtshan dang ldan pa'i dur khrod du //
NG0282:1927: gru gsum zla gam 'khor lo bri //
NG0282:1928: gru chad bar khyams sgo dang ldan //
NG0282:1929: las rnams ma lus kun bya ste //
NG0282:1930: bar chad bsal la rdzas rnams dgod //
NG0282:1931: lha lnga rdzas dang mar me dang *//
NG0282:1932: steng 'og rdzas rnams de bzhin dgram //
NG0282:1933: rim par bya ba gang yin pa'i //
NG0282:1934: ting 'dzin rab tu gsal bar bya //
NG0282:1935: lha lnga spyan drangs mchod pa dang *//
NG0282:1936: bstod dang 'dzabs snyen las rnams bya //
NG0282:1937: rigs lnga khrag 'thung bsgrub pa ste //
NG0282:1938: bar chad bsal zhing mtshan ma brtag / sgrub pa
NG0282:1939: chen po'i las kyi mchog / dus rnams kun tu
NG0282:1940: bar mi gcad // lha la mchod cing mkha' 'gro bskul //
NG0282:1941: mi 'gyur mtshan ma byung ba dang *//
NG0282:1942: dngos grub chen po'i lha lnga la //
NG0282:1943: rim par blang zhing dbang bskur bya //
NG0282:1944: rim par don dang ldan par bya //
NG0282:1945: thams cad kun la rnam par g.yengs //
NG0282:1946: don dang ldan pa'i dur khrod du //
NG0282:1948: bsrung ba'i rim pa ma lus bya //
NG0282:1949: thod pa mtshan ldan rangs po la //
NG0282:1950: gtso bo yab yum sngags bris la //
NG0282:1951: snying dang bcas pa dbus su dgod //
NG0282:1952: phyi ma'i rdzas rnams rim pas te //
NG0282:1953: mar me ye shes gcig tu 'dus //
NG0282:1954: dngos grub mtshan ldan ka pa lar //
NG0282:1955: yab yum sngags rnams bris nas ni //
NG0282:1956: gang yin gnas su dgod par bya //
NG0282:1957: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang yang dgod //
NG0282:1958: nus pa'i dbang yang sngon du bskur //
NG0282:1959: ting 'dzin rim pa grangs mang yang *//
NG0282:1960: thams cad 'dus pa'i yab yum bsgom //
NG0282:1961: spyan drangs rim pa de bzhin du //
NG0282:1962: las nyid grub pa'i snying por 'dus //
NG0282:1963: bya ba thams cad yongs su sbyar //
NG0282:1964: chos dbyings nam mkha'i ngo bo las //
NG0282:1965: cir yang snang ba lha yi sku //
NG0282:1966: gsal ba nyid la bsam du med //
NG0282:1967: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NG0282:1968: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs su gsol //
NG0282:1969: hum me long ye shes byin brlab las //
NG0282:1970: rang rig ye shes me bo che //
NG0282:1971: ma rig mun pa bsal du med //
NG0282:1972: thams cad rang byung ye shes me //
NG0282:1973: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs su gsol //
NG0282:1974: hum stong gsum thams cad gzhal yas khang *//
NG0282:1975: skye ba med par ye nas grub //
NG0282:1976: 'dzin pa med par rang bzhin grol //
NG0282:1979: hum 'khor ba ma spangs lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:1980: spangs na byang chub sems nyid spangs //
NG0282:1981: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NG0282:1982: rdzas kyang de bzhin rtogs pa'i ngang *//
NG0282:1983: dkyil 'khor rgyan du dgram par bya //
NG0282:1984: hum thams cad thig le ye brdal las //
NG0282:1985: re dang dogs pa'i sems spangs la //
NG0282:1986: rten yang ye brdal ka pa lar //
NG0282:1987: dur khrod rdzas su bzhag nas kyang *//
NG0282:1988: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs su gsol //
NG0282:1989: hum chos dbyings gsal la rtog pa med //
NG0282:1990: nyes pas ma bsgribs gsal ba'i 'od //
NG0282:1991: ting 'dzin chen po'i byin brlab las //
NG0282:1992: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dbyings //
NG0282:1993: hum chos dbyings nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NG0282:1994: rol pas 'byung lngar lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:1995: grub kyang rol pa 'dzin pa bral //
NG0282:1996: rten du 'gyur bas rnam par gsal //
NG0282:1997: hum dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0282:1998: rang byung ye shes bzhugs gnas su //
NG0282:1999: ma bsgribs gsal ba'i 'od po che //
NG0282:2000: rig pa rang shar gzhal yas su //
NG0282:2001: thig le cir yang snang ba shar //
NG0282:2002: hum rang byung ye shes gsal ba'i 'od //
NG0282:2003: rol pa bsam med brjod las 'das //
NG0282:2004: lha nyid gsal la gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:2005: bde ba chen po'i klong na bzhugs //
NG0282:2006: hum chos sku nyag gcig gnyis su med //
NG0282:2007: cir yang snang bas bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:2008: gang du gnas pa'i de bzhin nyid //
NG0282:2009: rang byung chen po'i dbyings na g.yos //
NG0282:2010: hum gsal la rtog med ye shes te //
NG0282:2011: ye shes chen po phyag rgya che //
NG0282:2012: rnam par grol cing dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:2013: chos dbyings dag pa'i phyag rgya 'byung *//
NG0282:2014: thig le byang chub sems nyid las //
NG0282:2015: thams cad dngos grub chen po yin //
NG0282:2016: chos dbyings nor bu rin po che //
NG0282:2017: zad pa med par thams cad 'byung *//
NG0282:2018: sku dang ye shes bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:2019: nyon mongs gdung ba sel bar mdzad //
NG0282:2020: zad pa med pa'i dngos grub gter //
NG0282:2021: re ba skong bas thams cad tshim //
NG0282:2022: dga' bar 'gyur bas rtogs pa skye //
NG0282:2023: rang byung lha la dngos grub slong *//
NG0282:2024: hum bsam pas 'grub pa'i rin po che //
NG0282:2025: zad pa med pa'i gter du gnas //
NG0282:2026: thams cad re skong bsam pa 'grub //
NG0282:2027: sku gsum sa thob dngos grub gter //
NG0282:2028: da lta nyid du stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2029: thugs dam chen po rgyud bskul na //
NG0282:2030: gang la thogs med dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:2031: hum rang byung ye shes lha la dngos grub slong *//
NG0282:2032: 'dir gshegs spyan 'dren dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:2033: nam mkha' bzhin du re dogs mi mnga' yang *//
NG0282:2034: thugs rje'i shugs kyis byin rlabs sprin dang 'dra //
NG0282:2035: bdud rtsi char chen 'bebs pas re ba skong *//
NG0282:2036: chos nyid re dogs bral ba'i rang bzhin las //
NG0282:2037: dngos grub stsal dang stsol bar mi dmigs kyang *//
NG0282:2038: byin rlab dbang gis dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2039: ye shes lha la re dogs ma mchis kyang *//
NG0282:2040: dogs pa'i sems dang mi cha re @#//
NG0282:2042: bsam pa 'grub pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2043: hum lha dang gnyis su med par gang gsal ba //
NG0282:2044: re ba'i dngos grub dang po de bas na //
NG0282:2045: lha la lha yis byin brlab nus pa can //
NG0282:2046: bstan pa rgyas pa'i phyir na slod lags kyis //
NG0282:2047: thogs pa med pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2048: hum dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi byin brlab las //
NG0282:2049: zhal bu mtshan ldan rdo rje ka pa lar //
NG0282:2050: 'chi med tshe yi g.yung drung ci bsam 'grub //
NG0282:2051: 'dun pa rigs kyi dngos grub mdzad med gter //
NG0282:2052: bdud 'dul lha nye bgegs zhi rab tu bzang *//
NG0282:2053: nye ba nyid du bsam pa da re ran //
NG0282:2054: yang dag ldan pa'i dngos grub dam pa 'di //
NG0282:2055: ci bsam 'grub cing re ba skong ba dang *//
NG0282:2056: rig 'dzin sa la nges par phyin pa dang */
NG0282:2057: thogs pa med par ci bsam 'grub pa dang *//
NG0282:2058: dngos grub dam pa de nyid stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2059: hum chos dbyings nam mkha' bsam med brjod las 'das //
NG0282:2060: thams cad 'byung zhing re ba thams cad skong *//
NG0282:2061: skong ba nyid na rgyal ba'i dbyings su thim //
NG0282:2062: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2063: hum byin rlabs chen po nam mkha'i sprin dang 'dra //
NG0282:2064: bdud dang srin po 'dul phyir rgyal ba'i rigs su byung *//
NG0282:2065: dbang bskur byin brlab nus pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:2066: sras kyi dam pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2067: hum thabs dang shes rab bde ba chen po'i dbyings //
NG0282:2068: yab la chags shing gnyis su med pa'i yum //
NG0282:2069: don dam ngang la rigs kyi yum du bstan //
NG0282:2070: zad pa med pa gter gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2071: hum gdug pa 'dul phyir yab kyi thugs las sprul //
NG0282:2072: dregs pa'i 'khor rnams ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NG0282:2073: 'dul ba'i dbang gis sprul pa cir yang ston //
NG0282:2074: gdug pa 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2075: yab la dgyes shing gnyis su med pa'i yum //
NG0282:2076: dregs pa yum du gyur pa 'dul mdzad pa //
NG0282:2077: re skong bdud 'dul dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2078: hum yab yum gnyis med sras kyi dam pa byung //
NG0282:2079: gdug pa sprul pa'i tshogs rnams 'dul mdzad pa //
NG0282:2080: yab yum rgyun du 'dzin cing las rnams grub //
NG0282:2081: thogs med sgrol ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:2082: las kyi bya ba thams cad kun //
NG0282:2083: de bzhin ma nor rim pa bzhin //
NG0282:2084: gnas skabs nyid du yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:2085: kun kyang don la rgyas par bstan //
NG0282:2086: rnam gnyis don la rnam par gtad //
NG0282:2088: bstan pa'i las nyid kun kyang 'grub //
NG0282:2089: dpal gyi dngos grub chen po ni //
NG0282:2090: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas su //
NG0282:2091: man+dal mda' gang byas nas su //
NG0282:2092: thig dang bri ba de bzhin bya //
NG0282:2093: phyi nang gsang gsum las kyi mchog / thod pa dmar nag dbang drag la //
NG0282:2094: snying po gdan dang bcas pa bri //
NG0282:2095: snying dang bcas pa'i rdzas dag @#//
NG0282:2097: bskyed dang spyan drang bstim mchod bstod //
NG0282:2098: dbus su dgod cing gsal bar bsam //
NG0282:2099: mar me gsol byang rgyan rnams dgod //
NG0282:2100: mchod pa'i rgyan yang de bzhin te //
NG0282:2101: ting 'dzin chen po'i byin brlab kyis //
NG0282:2102: rim par bsgom zhing gzhal yas khang *//
NG0282:2103: gru gsum zla gam mu khyud la //
NG0282:2104: thod pa skom rlon btang bar bsgom //
NG0282:2105: shar sgor bum bzhugs sgo ba'i tshul //
NG0282:2106: gtso bo'i zhal ni yum la gzigs //
NG0282:2107: spyan 'dren bstim dang mchod pa dang *//
NG0282:2108: bsnyen pa bstod dang mchod pa dbul //
NG0282:2109: mtshan ma brtan po byung ba dang *//
NG0282:2110: thod pa blang zhing mar me gso //
NG0282:2111: bar ma chad par de bzhin bya //
NG0282:2112: lha la bstod cing thugs dam bskul //
NG0282:2113: dngos grub chen po'i las rnams ni //
NG0282:2114: gnad la dbab cing mchod pa dbul //
NG0282:2115: lha la bslang zhing lan gsum bstims //
NG0282:2116: rdzas la blang ba de bzhin te //
NG0282:2117: rim pa bzhin du rab shes bya //
NG0282:2118: tha ma las kyi mtha' rnams rgyas //
NG0282:2119: yi ge 'khor lo'i sa non nas //
NG0282:2120: 'gro ba'i don rnams de bzhin bya //
NG0282:2121: rnam gnyis sku yi 'dul thabs bstan //
NG0282:2122: hum chos sku bde ba chen po'i ngang nyid las //
NG0282:2123: kun tu bzang po'i rol ba cir yang snang *//
NG0282:2124: bdud dang srin po ma lus 'dul ba'i lha //
NG0282:2125: rngam pa chen pos srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha //
NG0282:2126: bdud rgyal dregs pa 'dul zhing dbang du sdud //
NG0282:2127: hum dang phat kyi sgra 'byin stong gsum sgrol //
NG0282:2128: ya mtshan rmad du che ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2129: hum dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2130: dbu gsum rnam thar gsum gyi dbu //
NG0282:2131: dbus ni mthing gar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2132: chos kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa dang *//
NG0282:2133: zhe sdang rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2134: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i zhal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2135: g.yas ni dkar bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2136: chos kyi sku la nyes pa med pa dang *//
NG0282:2137: nyon mongs gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2138: nyes pa med pa'i zhal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2139: g.yon ni dmar bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2140: thugs rje thabs kyis chags pa dang *//
NG0282:2141: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2142: thugs rje chags pa'i zhal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2143: spyan mig dgu ru bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2145: theg pa dgu dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2146: 'khor ba 'joms pa'i spyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2147: mche ba bcu gnyis bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2148: skye mched bcu gnyis rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2149: sha za gdug pa'i mche ba dmar ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2150: skye mched rtsad nas gcod pa'i tshems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2151: shangs ni gsum du bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2152: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang *//
NG0282:2153: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2154: sku gsum lhun grub shangs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2155: zhal ni gsum du bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2156: dug gsum zhal du gsol ba dang *//
NG0282:2157: stong gsum sgra yis gang ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2160: ri spu gyen du 'khyil bar bstan pa ni /
NG0282:2161: khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba dang *//
NG0282:2162: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i sa la dgod pa'i phyir /
NG0282:2163: khams gsum 'dren pa'i ri spu nyid la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2164: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2165: gdug pa can rnams dbang du bsdu ba dang *//
NG0282:2166: srid pa'i rtse mo zil gyis gnon pa dang *//
NG0282:2167: gdug pa 'joms pa'i dbu+u la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2168: phyag drug ye shes drug gi rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2169: g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa ni //
NG0282:2170: sa dgu lhun gyis grub pa dang *//
NG0282:2171: theg pa dgu dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2172: sa dgu gnon pa'i phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2173: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa ni //
NG0282:2174: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa dang *//
NG0282:2175: rigs lnga 'gro ba'i don bya'i phyir //
NG0282:2176: ye shes lnga ldan phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2177: g.yon gyi dang po me dpung bsnams pa ni //
NG0282:2178: ye shes me ru 'bar ba dang *//
NG0282:2179: 'khor ba nyon mongs bsreg pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2180: ye shes 'bar ba'i phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2181: g.yon gyi bar ma kha t+wam rtse gsum bsnams par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2182: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa dang *//
NG0282:2183: rigs gsum mgon po rnams dang gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2184: dug gsum rtsad gcod phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2185: g.yas g.yon tha ma rdo rje ri rab phur bu 'dril bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2186: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa ste /
NG0282:2187: khams gsums gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2188: thabs dang shes rab phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2189: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la gsol ba ni //
NG0282:2190: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NG0282:2191: glang chen ko rlon sku la gsol bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2192: gti mug rtsad nas bcad nas kyang *//
NG0282:2193: thugs rje thabs dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2194: gti mug 'joms pa'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2195: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2196: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2197: thugs rje chags par ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2198: 'dod chags 'joms pa'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2199: stag gi sham thabs sku la brgyan pa ni //
NG0282:2200: zhe sdang rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2201: thugs rje thabs dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2202: zhe sdang rtsad gcod rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2203: thod pa rlon pas sku la brgyan pa ni //
NG0282:2204: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2205: skye ba med pa'i don ni grub pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2206: chos sku gnyis med rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2207: thod pa skam pos sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2208: longs spyod sku dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2209: thams cad kun tu longs sku bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:2210: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2211: thod pa tshal bus sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2212: sprul pa'i sku dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2213: sprul sku 'gro ba'i don du cir yang snang *//
NG0282:2215: sku gnyis med rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2216: zhag gi zo ris sku la brgyan pa ni //
NG0282:2217: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2218: mar me mdzad dang bstan pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2219: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2220: thal chen tshom bus sku la brgyan pa ni //
NG0282:2221: da ltar sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2222: bcom ldan 'das dang skal pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2223: da ltar sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2224: rak+ta'i thig les sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2225: ma byon sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2226: rgyal ba byams pa'i bstan pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2227: ma byon sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2228: rdo rje'i gshog pa sku la brgyan pa ni //
NG0282:2229: ma mo mkha' 'gro zil gyis gnon pa dang *//
NG0282:2230: thams cad kun tu dbang du sdud pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2231: rdo rje gshog pa'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2232: sbrul chen rigs bzhis sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2233: gdug pa klu rnams rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2234: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i rgyan ni rigs bzhir bstan pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2235: gdug pa chen po'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2236: zhabs bzhi mngon par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2237: rdzu 'phrul bzhi yi rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2238: g.yas gnyis bskum par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2239: pho gnyis 'gram pa brdzis pa dang *//
NG0282:2240: thabs ni shes rab rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2241: pho gnyis brdzis pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2242: g.yon gnyis brkyang bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2243: mo gnyis nu phrag brdzes pa ni //
NG0282:2244: shes rab thabs kyi rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2245: mo gnyis brdzis pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2246: rdo rje ba spu khro bos gtams par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2247: 'jigs pa med par dbang du sdud pa dang *//
NG0282:2248: thams cad kun tu sprul pas khyab pa dang *//
NG0282:2249: 'jigs med khro bo 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2250: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:2251: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang *//
NG0282:2252: rngam brjid chen po rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NG0282:2253: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2254: zhe sdang tshul yis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0282:2255: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2256: yab kyi thugs dam gnyen po bskong ba'i yum //
NG0282:2257: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs dgyes pa skong ba'i yum //
NG0282:2258: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gtso mo chen mo ste //
NG0282:2259: dgyes pa skong ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2260: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing *//
NG0282:2261: g.yas pa dgyes pas yab la 'khyud //
NG0282:2262: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NG0282:2263: rdo rje rigs kyi yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2264: sku mdog mthing bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2265: 'gyur ba med pa'i rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2266: thams cad chos sku gcig pa dang *//
NG0282:2267: don rnams thams cad thugs su chud pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2268: 'gyur ba med pa'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2271: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa dang *//
NG0282:2273: thabs dang shes rab spyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2274: zhal ni gcig tu bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2275: yab la dgyes par bzhad pa dang *//
NG0282:2276: dug lnga zhal du gsol ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2277: yab la dgyes pa'i zhal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2278: mche ba bzhi ru bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2279: skye ba rnam bzhi rtsad nas gcod pa dang *//
NG0282:2280: gdug pa'i tshems 'dra rngam pa'i sha za'i phyir //
NG0282:2281: skye shi rtsad gcod tshems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2282: shangs ni gcig tu bstan pa dang *//
NG0282:2283: dri yi mchod pas mnyes pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2284: chos nyid gcig pa'i shangs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2285: g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa ni //
NG0282:2286: shes rab thabs la chags pa dang *//
NG0282:2287: dgyes pa chen po bskang ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2288: shes rab thabs la chags pa'i phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2289: g.yon na b+han+da rak+ta bsnams pa ni //
NG0282:2290: yum gyi chags pa sel ba dang *//
NG0282:2291: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2292: chags pa sel ba'i phyag la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2293: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la gsol ba ni //
NG0282:2294: sdug bsngal brgyad po rtsad nas bcad nas kyang *//
NG0282:2295: rnam pa thams cad chos nyid dbyings su sgrol //
NG0282:2296: sdug bsngal 'joms pa'i rgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2297: zhabs gnyis mngon par bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2298: rkang gnyis kun la brtse bar dgongs pa dang *//
NG0282:2299: bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs dam dgyes skong phyir //
NG0282:2300: rkang gnyis brtse dgongs zhabs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2301: 'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0282:2302: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2303: hum khro bo chen po hum ka ra //
NG0282:2304: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2305: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na mda' gzhu bsnams //
NG0282:2306: tshabs pa 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2307: steng gi za byed rdo rje sgra 'byin ma //
NG0282:2308: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag / 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshangs mo'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0282:2309: tshabs rigs 'bul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2310: phag gi mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2311: tshangs pa po yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2312: 'dul ba'i dbang du phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2313: gdug rtsub klu bdud khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2314: smig bu'i mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2315: tshangs pa mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2316: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na mda' gzhu bsnams //
NG0282:2317: so rno grims bzhed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2318: hum khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal //
NG0282:2319: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2320: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tri shul 'khor lo bsnams //
NG0282:2321: brgya byin 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2322: shar gyi za byed rdo rje rnam snyems ma //
NG0282:2323: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag / 'dul ba'i dbang gis brgya byin mo yi
NG0282:2326: brgya byin 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2327: stag gi mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2328: brgya byin pho yi 'khor gyi gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2329: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2330: gdug pa 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2331: bya rgod mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2332: brgya byin mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2333: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2334: zhi ba chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2335: hum shar lho'i khro bo dbyug sngon po //
NG0282:2336: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2337: 'dul ba'i dbang gis dbyug to me dpung bsnams //
NG0282:2338: drang srong 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2339: shar lho za byed chen mo rdo rje sder mo la //
NG0282:2340: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag /
NG0282:2341: 'dul ba'i dbang gis drang srong mo yi gdan la

NG0282:2343: g.yag gi mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2344: drang srong pho yi 'khor gyi gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2345: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2346: rdzi rnon brjed med khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2347: bya rog mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2348: drang srong mo yi 'khor gyis gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2349: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2350: tshe gsum dran byed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2351: hum lho yi khro bo gshin rje'i gshed //
NG0282:2352: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //

NG0282:2354: gshin rje 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //

NG0282:2357: 'dul ba'i dbang gis gshin rje mo yi gdan la
NG0282:2358: bzhugs // gshin rje 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2359: sha ba'i mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2360: gshin rje pho yi 'khor gyi gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2361: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2362: smyos par byed pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2363: 'ug pa'i mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2364: gshin rje mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2365: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2366: rtogs pa skyed byed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2367: hum lho nub khro bo mi g.yo mgon //
NG0282:2368: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2369: 'dul ba'i dbang gis ral gri zhags pa bsnams //
NG0282:2370: srin po 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2371: lho nub za byed rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NG0282:2372: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag / 'dul ba'i dbang gis srin mo'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0282:2373: srin mo 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2374: gzig gi mgo can yab kyi pho nya ste //
NG0282:2376: gdul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2379: khwa ta'i mgo can sum gyi pho nya ste //
NG0282:2381: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2382: 'dzin cing bsam pas slob pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2383: hum nub kyi khro bo rta mgrin dpal //
NG0282:2384: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2385: 'dul ba'i dbang gis zhags pa spu gri bsnams //
NG0282:2386: klu bdud 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2387: nub kyi za byed rdo rje gtum mo ni //
NG0282:2388: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag /
NG0282:2389: 'dul ba'i dbang gis klu bdud mo yi gdan la

NG0282:2391: byi la'i mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2392: klu bdud pho yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2393: 'dul ba'i dbang gi phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2394: gdug pa so rnon ci la thogs med khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2395: pu shud mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2396: klu bdud mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2397: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2398: 'jigs byed glog gcod khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2399: hum nub byang khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NG0282:2400: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2401: 'dul ba'i dbang gis rdul g.yab ba dan bsnams //
NG0282:2402: rlung lha 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2403: nub byang za byed rdo rje mda' snyems ma //
NG0282:2404: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag /
NG0282:2405: 'dul ba'i dbang gis rlung lha mo yi gdan la
NG0282:2406: bzhugs // rlung lha 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2407: spyang ki'i mgo can yab kyi pho nya ste //
NG0282:2408: rlung lha pho yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2409: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2410: gsod par byed pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NG0282:2411: khra yi mgo na yum gyi pho nya ste //
NG0282:2412: rlung lha mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2413: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2414: gsod par byed pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2415: hum byang gi khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NG0282:2416: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2417: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na rgya gram bsnams //
NG0282:2418: gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2419: byang gi za byed yum chen rlung 'byin ma //
NG0282:2420: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud //
NG0282:2421: 'dul ba'i dbang gis gnod sbyin mo yi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0282:2422: gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2423: seng ge'i mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2424: gnod sbyin pho yi 'khor gyi gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2425: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2426: stobs chen 'gro mgyogs khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2427: pha wang mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2428: gnod sbyin mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2429: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2432: hum byang shar khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal //
NG0282:2433: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2434: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na rdo rje mda' gzhu bsnams //
NG0282:2435: dbang ldan 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2436: byang shar za byed rdo rje gsod byed ma //
NG0282:2437: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud pa'i phyag /
NG0282:2438: 'dul ba'i dbang gis dbang ldan mo yi gdan la
NG0282:2439: bzhugs // dbang ldan 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2440: dred kyi mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2441: dbang ldan 'dul ba'i 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2442: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2443: 'jigs med shugs chen zhe sdang khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2444: sre mo'i mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2445: dbang ldan mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2446: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2447: bde mgyogs sha grims 'gugs byed khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2448: hum 'og gi khro bo stobs po che //
NG0282:2449: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NG0282:2450: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tho ba gtun shing bsnams //
NG0282:2451: sa bdag 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2452: 'og gi za byed rdo rje bskyod ma ni //
NG0282:2453: zhal gcig phyag gnyis yab la 'khyud //
NG0282:2454: 'dul ba'i dbang gis sa bdag mo yi gdan la bzhugs //
NG0282:2455: sa bdag 'dul ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2456: dom gyi mgo can yab kyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2457: sa bdag pho yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2458: 'dus pa'i dbang gis phyag na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:2459: dmigs dang khraus pa brjed med khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2460: byi ba'i mgo can yum gyi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:2461: sa bdag mo yi 'khor na gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2462: 'dul ba'i dbang gis phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:2463: 'bigs byed sgrol bar byed pa khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2464: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:2465: rdzas la brten te sgrub pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o
NG0282:2466: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das dur khrod kyi
NG0282:2467: bdag po bdud rtsi chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la
NG0282:2469: gnas ni dur khrod gzhal yas su //
NG0282:2470: bar snang dmar dang gnag pa dang *//
NG0282:2471: ri yang dmar nag rdo rje'i dbyibs //
NG0282:2472: me tog shing dang lo 'dab rgyas //
NG0282:2473: sman rnams 'khrungs dang sa bzang dang *//
NG0282:2474: gong du bstan pa'i nges pa med //
NG0282:2475: rtsa ba lo mar bcas pa skam //
NG0282:2476: yum yang yid du 'ong ba btsal //
NG0282:2477: rigs btsun ngang bzang shongs yangs che //
NG0282:2478: lcang lo'i skra la sked pa phra //
NG0282:2479: smra ba snyan la rna ba gsang *//
NG0282:2480: smin mtshams bar ma chad pa dang *//
NG0282:2481: so thags dam la shangs kyang mdzes //
NG0282:2482: stod smad snyoms la nu ma 'bur //
NG0282:2483: nyes pa'i skyon rnams med par bya //
NG0282:2484: nyid las mi gzhan mchod pa stobs //
NG0282:2485: nyams pa thogs med spyod nus dang *//
NG0282:2486: bar chad sel zhing nyes pa med //
NG0282:2489: shes bzhin yid 'ong stobs ldan dang *//
NG0282:2491: dam tshig gtsang ma dam pa bsrungs //
NG0282:2492: smra nyung don chen dngos grub snod //
NG0282:2493: 'dzin pas ma bcings lta ba rtogs //
NG0282:2494: bsam gtan don dang mi 'bral ba'i //
NG0282:2495: snying rje'i sems dang ldan pa yis //
NG0282:2496: 'dam zhing nyes pa bsal bar bya //
NG0282:2497: ston pa chen po'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:2498: thugs rje nam mkha'i cho 'phrul gyis //
NG0282:2499: thams cad bdud rtsi sa la bab //
NG0282:2500: 'byung ba chen po'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:2501: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin te //
NG0282:2502: phyi nang rtsa ba brgyad po dang *//
NG0282:2503: gsang ba nyid du de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:2504: byang chub sems dang mam sa dang *//
NG0282:2505: dri chen rak+ta dri chu rnams //
NG0282:2506: sder chags sha dang rmig zlum sha / kha brag
NG0282:2507: sha dang 'dab chags sha / rkang leb sha yang
NG0282:2508: de bzhin bshams // lan tshwa brag zhun lag pa dang *//
NG0282:2509: cong zhi rab tu rnam pa lnga //
NG0282:2510: debazhin rim las yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:2512: dam rdzas lnga yis chag chag gdab //
NG0282:2513: om hum bo d+hi tsit+ta man+dal hum //
NG0282:2514: om ku ku man+da la hum /
NG0282:2515: om ma ha mam sa man+da la hum /
NG0282:2517: om g+han d+ha man+da la hum /
NG0282:2518: lug dang spyang ki'i sog pa la //
NG0282:2519: gtso bo nyid du yang dag bshad //
NG0282:2520: spyan dang bstim la mchod bstod bya //
NG0282:2521: sog pa'i rgyab tu sgo srung bri //
NG0282:2522: hum rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NG0282:2523: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NG0282:2524: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NG0282:2525: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NG0282:2526: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NG0282:2527: gtogs shing grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NG0282:2528: sgo yi g.yas su gdags par bya /
NG0282:2529: khyi dang phag gi sog pa la //
NG0282:2530: dam sri bris la las rnams bya //
NG0282:2531: sgo yi g.yon du gdags par bya //
NG0282:2533: dbul zhing dregs pa kun kyang mchod //
NG0282:2534: rdo rje phur pa'i dam sri mnan //
NG0282:2535: gsum pa tshogs bsag sgrib sbyang bya //
NG0282:2536: de nas thig ni gdab par bya //
NG0282:2537: sa thig gnam thig de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:2538: tshon yang de bzhin shes par bya //
NG0282:2539: bri ba'i rim pa 'di lta ste //
NG0282:2540: gru gsum zla gam mu khyud dang *//
NG0282:2541: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi rtsibs brgyad dang *//
NG0282:2542: gru chad bzhi dang lha rnams dang *//
NG0282:2543: sgo dang rta babs bcas pa dang *//
NG0282:2544: bum pa 'khor lo gdugs dang bcas //
NG0282:2545: gru gsum dmar dang gnag dang bcas //
NG0282:2546: gnag dang yang ni thod pa dkar //
NG0282:2547: rigs dang dmar ba gnag pa dkar //
NG0282:2548: ser dang ljang dang gru chad dmar //
NG0282:2549: ser las rigs dang mthun par bri //
NG0282:2550: rtsigs pa gzhi mar thod pa dkar //
NG0282:2551: gzhi ser lhu dum dmar ba dang *//
NG0282:2552: ljang la rgyu zhags dkar ba dang *//
NG0282:2553: rin chen lnga yang rnam par gtang //
NG0282:2554: rin chen phreng ba dkar po gtang //
NG0282:2555: lcags ri nag po me ri dmar //

NG0282:2585: phyi yi rim par dgod par bya //
NG0282:2586: yang na 'di ltar bshad par bya //
NG0282:2587: cong zi dang ni lan tshwa dang *//
NG0282:2588: ra mo shag dang ram nye ba //
NG0282:2589: brag zhun brag rgya ha'o gnyis //

NG0282:2591: gsang ba'i rim par de bzhin dgod //

NG0282:2593: yab yum bzhi bzhi rnam pa brgyad //

NG0282:2595: gzhi yi rnam lnga ma 'khrul na //
NG0282:2596: ji ltar bye yang nges par med /
NG0282:2597: kha dog ro dang dbyibs rnams dang *//

NG0282:2601: khro bo drag po'i tsham rngams bya //
NG0282:2602: mtshams gyis nyes pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2603: las kyi lha yi ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0282:2604: dbus kyi thod pa stong par 'gyur //
NG0282:2605: 'jigs pa'i stong pa chen po yin //
NG0282:2607: sngags kyi gtso bo nyid du gnas //

NG0282:2609: spyan dang bstim dang sngags kyi las //
NG0282:2610: bstod cing thod pa de bzhin blang *//

NG0282:2673: phyogs mtshams brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:2674: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:2675: om badzra kro d+ha hum ka ra hum gardza gardza hum phat /

NG0282:2678: hum thugs rje chen po'i ngang nyid las //

NG0282:2681: 'khor ba'i bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //

NG0282:2689: bam hum phat / sid+d+hi sid+d+hi sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /

NG0282:2691: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NG0282:2693: nga la bar chad byed rnams //
NG0282:2694: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par gyis //
NG0282:2695: las rnams thams cad bsrung ba yi //
NG0282:2696: las sngags thams cad kun bsdus nas //
NG0282:2697: bar du gcod pa'i 'byung po la //
NG0282:2698: gsang ba yang dag mtshams su bshad //
NG0282:2700: las ma lus mthar byung ba //
NG0282:2701: nus pa yod par bya ba'i phyir //
NG0282:2702: sngon du dbang bskur yang dag bshad //
NG0282:2703: bdud rtsi lnga yi thod pa la //
NG0282:2704: byin brlab 'byung zhing bstim pa dang *//
NG0282:2705: bsgo dang brda phyag dam sri mnan //
NG0282:2707: stangs stabs rtags kyi rim pa yis //
NG0282:2708: lha dang don gyis gnyis su med //
NG0282:2709: thod pa'i lha rnams gsal ba la //
NG0282:2710: spyan drangs nam mkhar rab tu bzhugs //
NG0282:2711: sngags kyi bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'bab //
NG0282:2712: tha mar rang nyid thim par gyur //
NG0282:2713: bdud rtsi mu tig dri ma med //
NG0282:2714: thams cad de yi rang bzhin no //
NG0282:2715: las kyi bya ba kun byas nas //
NG0282:2716: bdag gzhan gnyis su rnam par gyur //
NG0282:2718: nam mkha' gnas pa'i sbyor ba las //
NG0282:2719: byang sems mu tig rnam par thim //
NG0282:2720: de yang mu tig dri med 'dra //
NG0282:2721: yang nas yang du 'gyur bas na //
NG0282:2722: de nyid bdud rtsi chen po yin //
NG0282:2723: dbus nas gzung te shar dag tu //
NG0282:2724: rim pa lnga ni rang byung lnga //
NG0282:2725: phyogs mtshams ra sa ya na la //

NG0282:2727: lnga nas bzung zhing yab yum spel //
NG0282:2728: rgyan bstar me long g.yab mo bya //

NG0282:2756: a mr-i ta kun+da li hu~m tha /
NG0282:2757: phyogs mtshams thod pa'i sman rnams la //
NG0282:2758: rim pa bzhin du yang dag bzlas //
NG0282:2759: lha la bstod cing srung ma bskul //
NG0282:2760: mchod pa 'bul zhing bar gcod bsal //
NG0282:2761: lnga'am bdun du de nyid sbyar //
NG0282:2762: dkar ba sngo dang dmar ba dang *//
NG0282:2763: ljang dang mthing ba rnam par byung *//
NG0282:2764: sha rtsi dkar la sngo bsangs mdog / dmar la cha phra ljang la ldem //
NG0282:2765: mthing ga skra bzang rdo rje'i dbyibs //
NG0282:2766: mngar dang kha ba'i dri dag dang *//
NG0282:2767: skyur ba tsha ba yang dag 'byung *//
NG0282:2768: ngad pa'i dri rnams de bzhin no //
NG0282:2771: brtul zhugs che zhing shes rab gsal //
NG0282:2772: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dag dang *//
NG0282:2773: rin chen pad+ma las kyi rigs //
NG0282:2774: rdo rje'i rigs dang yang dag don //
NG0282:2775: de nyid dus na lnga ru snang *//
NG0282:2777: rgya gram rdo rje yang dag 'byung *//
NG0282:2778: de bzhin rin chen pad+ma dang *//
NG0282:2779: las dang rdo rje'i rigs rnams kyis //
NG0282:2780: khro bo lnga yi dngos grub blang *//
NG0282:2781: che ba'i lus dang nag po'i 'od //
NG0282:2782: log pa'i sgra dang gnyis pa'i las //
NG0282:2783: grangs med sprul pa 'gyed pa dang *//
NG0282:2784: yi dam lha la mkha' 'gro'i gzugs //
NG0282:2785: dngos grub ster dang snyan pa'i glu //

NG0282:2787: nyi ma'i mdangs dang 'ja' tshon gzugs //
NG0282:2788: byis pa'i sems dang log pa'i rtags //
NG0282:2789: phur pa nyung dkar tho ba dang *//

NG0282:2795: dpa' brtul spyod pa dus dang sbyar //

NG0282:2802: nyes pa med pa'i rtags la dbab //

NG0282:2807: a las zla ba'i gtan pa la //

NG0282:2809: brdungs bas thab dang shes rab kyis //
NG0282:2810: nyes pa brdung ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NG0282:2811: sman nyid byang sems dri ma med //

NG0282:2813: rnam par rgyal ba nyid kyang rung *//
NG0282:2814: sngags nyid gang bsgoms de bzhin sbyar //

NG0282:2821: yab dang yum du bcas pa dang *//
NG0282:2822: rgyan dang cha lugs rab tu bstan //

NG0282:2833: dar ram za 'og snod du blug / phur pa bcug la rgya yang gdab *//
NG0282:2834: sras mchog rgya yang de bzhin gdab //
NG0282:2835: gdags shing kha sbyar nang du @#//

NG0282:2840: sbyin sreg gtang zhing bar chad bsal //
NG0282:2841: yab yum bar du bcug byas nas //
NG0282:2842: gu gul du bas de bzhin bdug / dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NG0282:2843: bcom ldan badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:2844: snang srid bdud rtsir byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:2845: rtsa ba brgyad dang yan lag stong *//
NG0282:2846: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0282:2847: pho brang chen po'i dbus su skyil //
NG0282:2848: rigs rnams bsdus nas dbus su gzhug / dbu mang phyag mang gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:2849: dbus su brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0282:2851: las kyi bya ba kun kyang bya //
NG0282:2852: til chen me mar rgyun mi gcad //
NG0282:2853: ye shes lnga yi me btang la //
NG0282:2854: rigs gcig bsgrub pa bar mi gcad //
NG0282:2855: mchod pa dus su dbul bya zhing *//
NG0282:2856: sbyor ba chen po de dus bya //
NG0282:2857: rgyu mchog mtshan dang ldan pa bsgral //
NG0282:2858: mchod pa dus su me mchod bya //
NG0282:2859: dam tshig zol zog med par bya //
NG0282:2860: lha la bstod cing srung ma bskul //
NG0282:2861: me dang du ba brlangs pa dang *//
NG0282:2862: dri dang lha mo mngon du ston //
NG0282:2863: mang du 'phel ba rdzas kyi mchog / bsgral dang chas pa'i dngos grub dang *//
NG0282:2864: lung bstan rdo rje rigs kyi bsgrub //
NG0282:2865: de la ya mtshan yongs mi bya //
NG0282:2866: re bas bar chod dogs pa 'byung *//
NG0282:2867: nyams su lon na nyam nga med //
NG0282:2868: nyam nga med na dngos grub myur //
NG0282:2869: dngos grub chen po re dogs bcas //
NG0282:2870: bdud dang cha brtags rab tu gces //

NG0282:2872: yid dam lha dang mkha' 'gro dang *//

NG0282:2879: thabs kyis spyod pas 'gro don du //

NG0282:2881: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad nas //
NG0282:2882: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig / om badzra ki li ki la ya /

NG0282:2888: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NG0282:2889: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NG0282:2890: sku yi dbyig tu bdag skyed cig / rak+ta kha hi /
NG0282:2891: om badzra ki li ki la ya /
NG0282:2894: khro chen nyi shu rtsa gcig dang *//
NG0282:2895: sngags dang dbyangs las 'byung ba ste //
NG0282:2896: rim pas blangs pa kun la sbyar //
NG0282:2897: lha dang rdzas kyi rim pa gnyis //
NG0282:2898: lha la gsum ste ma lus thim //
NG0282:2899: rdzas la brten pa'i bro dang sngags //
NG0282:2900: brgyad dang rgyun gdon par bya //
NG0282:2901: tshe bstim bkra shis las rnams bya //
NG0282:2902: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NG0282:2903: thams cad bcud ldan rdo rje nyid //
NG0282:2906: sa rnams rim par bgrod pa'o //
NG0282:2907: hum rdo rje bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor du //
NG0282:2908: mar me lnga brgyad dag la mdangs phyung nas //
NG0282:2909: rdo rje phur pa dag la dam bcas nas //
NG0282:2910: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs kyi byin rlabs las //
NG0282:2911: ye shes me yi 'od chen rab tu 'bar //
NG0282:2912: rtag tu snang ba'i go 'byed mar me bltams //
NG0282:2913: ma rig mun pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2914: ngan song 'khor ba'i gnas nas thar bar shog /
NG0282:2915: hum phyogs kyi sras mchog bzhi yi thugs kyi byin
NG0282:2916: rlabs las // ye shes me yi 'od chen rab tu 'bar //

NG0282:2930: // ye shes me 'od rab tu gsal ba dang *//

NG0282:2935: // ye shes me yi 'od chen rab tu gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2936: rtag tu snang ba'i go 'byed mar me bltams //

NG0282:2940: // ye shes me yi 'od chen rab tu gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2941: rtag tu snang ba'i go 'byed mar me bltams //

NG0282:2943: ngan song rgyud gsum gnas nas thar bar shog /
NG0282:2944: hu~m rig 'dzin rgyal po thugs kyi byin rlabs las
NG0282:2945: // ye shes me yi 'od chen rab tu 'bar //
NG0282:2946: rtag tu snang ba'i go 'byed mar me bltams //
NG0282:2947: ma rig mun pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2948: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi'i gnas nas 'dren par shog / hum 'khor ba'i mun pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:2949: don dam chos dbyings mthong ba dang *//
NG0282:2950: chu bo bzhi las brgal ba dang *//
NG0282:2951: bla med gnas su 'dren pa'i phyir //
NG0282:2952: mar me gsal ba'i 'od dbyung ngo *//
NG0282:2953: hum rin chen gser gyi sa gzhi la //
NG0282:2954: sa yi lha mo brtan ma ni //
NG0282:2955: btso ma gser gyi kha dog 'dra //
NG0282:2956: bdud rtsi'i bum pa phyag na bsnams //
NG0282:2957: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi mthar byung nas //
NG0282:2958: 'dod yon lha mor byin brlabs pa'i //
NG0282:2959: dam rdzas mang po'i gtor ma 'di //
NG0282:2960: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NG0282:2961: skyon med rdzas kyi gter sbas pas //
NG0282:2962: gser gyi sa gzhi'i yon tan dang *//
NG0282:2963: sa yi lha mo'i byin rlabs @#//
NG0282:2965: sgrub mchog bdag gi byin rlabs kyis //
NG0282:2966: zad med gter la longs spyod cing *//
NG0282:2967: 'dod yon mang po'i dbang thob nas //
NG0282:2968: rin chen lnga la dbang bsgyur shog / hum rdo rje phur pa bdud rtsi mchog gi sku //
NG0282:2969: rngam pa chen po'i rigs gcig bsgrub pa'i lha //
NG0282:2970: dbu ni bcu gsum gang la gang 'dul bstan //
NG0282:2971: g.yas dang g.yon du med par thams cad mthing *//
NG0282:2972: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2973: spyan ni sum cu so dgu byung ba ni //
NG0282:2974: thams cad kun tu khyab pa'i spyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2975: mche ba lnga bcu rtsa gnyis bsnol ba ni /
NG0282:2976: khams gsum gdug pa thams cad sgrol bar byed //
NG0282:2977: skye shi'i rtsa ba gcod pa'i tshems la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2978: shangs ni rnam pa bcu gsum byung ba ni //
NG0282:2979: dri rnams mchod pas mnyes byed cing *//
NG0282:2980: bde bar gshegs pa'i shangs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2981: ral pa gyen du 'khyil bar bstan pa ni //
NG0282:2983: byams pa'i mgon mdzad khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2984: g.yas g.yon dang po hum mdzad yab yum bsnams pa ni //
NG0282:2985: tshangs pa dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:2986: nyi ma zla ba 'dul ba khyod la bstod //
NG0282:2987: de yi 'og mas rnam rgyal yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:2988: dri za dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:2989: brgya byin 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2990: de yi 'og mas dbyug sngon yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:2991: drang srong dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:2992: me lha 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2993: de yi 'og mas gshin rje yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:2994: ma mo dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:2995: gshin rje 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2996: de yi 'og mas mi g.yo mgon po yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:2997: bden gral dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:2998: srin po 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:2999: de yi 'og mas rta mgrin yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:3000: bdud rnams dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:3001: klu rnams 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3002: de yi 'og mas gzhan gyis mi thub yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:3003: nor srung dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:3004: rlung lha 'dus pa'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3005: de yi 'og mas bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:3006: 'chi bdag dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:3007: gnod sbyin 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3008: de yi 'og mas khams gsum rnam rgyal yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:3009: bgegs rigs dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:3010: dbang ldan 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3011: de yi 'og mas stobs chen yab yum bsnams //
NG0282:3012: klu rnams dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen @#//
NG0282:3014: sa bdag 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3015: g.yas g.yon tha mas sras mchog drug bsnams shing *//
NG0282:3016: 'gro drug dbang sdud bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs //
NG0282:3017: 'jig rten 'dul ba'i lha chen drug la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3018: thod pa tshar gsum sku gsum lhun grub rtags //
NG0282:3019: zhag gi zo ris don dam bcud kyi rtags //
NG0282:3020: rak+ta'i thig le thugs rje chags pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3021: thal chen tshom bu thams cad mkhyen pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3022: glang chen ko shun thugs rje stobs kyi rtags //
NG0282:3023: zhing chen g.yang gzhi 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3024: stag gi sham bu dpal rtul zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3025: sbrul chen rigs bzhi klu yi rigs rnams dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3026: rdo rje'i gshog pa 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3027: zhabs brgyad phyogs mtshams dregs pa gnon pa'i rtags //
NG0282:3028: 'jig rten dpa' stong thams cad 'dul ba'i lha //
NG0282:3029: rdo rje phur pa bdud rtsi 'bebs mdzad lha //
NG0282:3030: bdud rtsi chen po'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3031: thams cad 'dul ba'i lha chen khyod la bstod //
NG0282:3032: bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:3033: bdud rtsi chen po 'di dag kyang *//
NG0282:3034: skyon yon rab tu che bas na //
NG0282:3035: bsrung ba'i rim pa tshul bzhin bya //
NG0282:3036: mtshan ma sha mdangs phyed par gyis //
NG0282:3037: chos nyid blta ba chen po yis //
NG0282:3038: ngan pa thams cad bzang por 'gyur //
NG0282:3039: de phyir rtogs pa rab tu gces //
NG0282:3040: ma rtogs 'khrul pa rtogs pa bsgom //
NG0282:3041: rang rgyud bral ba'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0282:3042: bar chad gtan nas 'joms par byed //
NG0282:3043: stong pa chen po'i ting 'dzin la //
NG0282:3044: bsod nams stong pa'i rang bzhin yin //
NG0282:3045: de nyid yang dag don shes na //
NG0282:3047: 'dzin pas bcings pa'i sems nyid ni //
NG0282:3049: rtags kyi bye brag ma phyed par //
NG0282:3050: dngos grub yal bar gtong ba dang *//
NG0282:3051: bdud kyi las las grub par byed //
NG0282:3052: rtsi med bdud kyi las su 'gyur //
NG0282:3053: de bzhin cha rtags rab tu gces //
NG0282:3054: sngon gyi bdud kyi rgyal po yang *//
NG0282:3055: gab sbas sha mdangs ma phyed par //
NG0282:3056: khams gsum sdug bsngal chen por gyur //
NG0282:3057: thar pa'i dus med thugs rjes bsgral //
NG0282:3058: sbyor dang sgrol ba ma rtogs te //
NG0282:3059: rang dgar bzung ba'i sbyor sgrol gyis //
NG0282:3060: rnam pa gnyis su smin par 'gyur //
NG0282:3061: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3062: sman sgrub pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o // // de
NG0282:3063: nas bcom ldan 'das rdzas thams cad khro bos bsgrub
NG0282:3064: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:3065: dur khrod chen po bstan pa bzhin //
NG0282:3066: man+dal bri ba de bzhin te //
NG0282:3067: mang nyung grangs su bshad pa tsam //
NG0282:3068: mtshan ldan lnga ru bshams pa'i rdzas //
NG0282:3069: bstan pa de bzhin mang nyung med //
NG0282:3070: bskyed dang spyan drang bstim pa dang *//
NG0282:3073: hum dbus kyi b+han d+ha sul med du //
NG0282:3074: byang chub sems la sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3075: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa rnams //
NG0282:3076: badzra ki la ya ru byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3077: rang byung bdud rtsi sman sbyar nas /  / rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3078: dbus su brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:3079: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:3080: om badzra ki li ki la ya sarba big+h+nam bam hum phat /
NG0282:3081: a mr-i ta kun+da li hum tha /

NG0282:3085: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa rnams /
NG0282:3086: khro bo rnam par rgyal dang byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3087: rang byung bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3088: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3089: shar du brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:3090: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //

NG0282:3094: hum lho yi b+han d+ha sul mar du //
NG0282:3095: mam sa mchog la sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3096: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa rnams //
NG0282:3097: khro bo gshin rje'i gshed du byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3098: rang byung bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3099: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3100: lho ru brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:3101: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:3102: om badzra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka hum /
NG0282:3103: pa tsa pa tsa hum phat /
NG0282:3104: a mr-i ta kun+da li hum tha /
NG0282:3106: hum nub kyi bun d+ha zla gam du //
NG0282:3107: rak+ta mchog la sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3108: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa rnams //
NG0282:3109: khro bo rta mgrin dpal du byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3110: rang byung bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3111: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3112: nub tu brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:3113: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:3114: om badzra kro d+ha ha ya gri wa hum hu lu hu lu hum phat /
NG0282:3115: om a mr-i ta kun+da li hum tha /
NG0282:3117: hum byang gi b+han d+ha rgya gram du //
NG0282:3118: dri chu mchog la sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3119: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa rnams //
NG0282:3120: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil par byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3121: rang byung bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3122: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3123: byang du brtan par bzhugs nas kyang *//
NG0282:3124: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol / om badzra kro d+ha a mr-i ta kun+da li hum /
NG0282:3126: a mr-i ta kun+da li hum tha /
NG0282:3128: hum rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag / bdud rtsi lnga dang rtsa ba brgyad //
NG0282:3129: yan lag stong dang rab bsnyams pa'i //
NG0282:3130: me tog rin chen lnga rnams dang *//
NG0282:3132: mtshams bzhi steng 'og byin brlabs nas //
NG0282:3133: rang byung bdud rtsi'i sman sbyar nas //
NG0282:3134: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskang *//
NG0282:3135: mtshams bzhi steng 'og brtan par bzhugs //
NG0282:3136: rang byung bdud rtsi'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:3137: hum badzra kro d+ha hum ka ra hum gardza gardza hum phat /
NG0282:3138: a mr-i ta kun+da li hum phat /
NG0282:3142: rim pa gang du bshad pas na //
NG0282:3143: khro bo las kyi bdud rtsi rnams //
NG0282:3144: mi bsre rang rang bsten par bya //
NG0282:3145: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3146: khro bo bdud rtsi bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0282:3147: / de nas bcom ldan 'das sman rigs gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:3148: mtshan ldan dur khrod gnas dag tu //
NG0282:3149: srung ba'i las rnams kun byas nas //
NG0282:3150: man+dal mda' gang gru bzhi la //
NG0282:3151: las kyi bya ba byas nas kyang *//
NG0282:3152: thig dang tshon yang de bzhin bya //
NG0282:3153: bri ba'i las nyid yang dag bshad //
NG0282:3154: gru gsum zla gam sgo dag bcas //
NG0282:3155: zlum po brtsig pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:3156: shar du sgo yang de bzhin te //
NG0282:3157: rim pas bskor ba'i me ri bya //
NG0282:3158: gdan dang snying po de bzhin brtag / sgo la yum gyi snying po bkod //
NG0282:3159: phyi nang gsang ba'i lnga gsum dang *//
NG0282:3160: rtsa ba brgyad kyang de bzhin du //
NG0282:3161: thams cad bdud rtsi bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NG0282:3162: mtshan ldan thod pa dri yis bdug / sman rnams nang du blug byas la //
NG0282:3163: srung ba'i las nyid yang dag bshad //
NG0282:3164: las kyi ting 'dzin chen po yis //
NG0282:3165: stong pa hum dang rdo rje dang *//
NG0282:3166: brgyad po nyid du yang dag 'gyur //
NG0282:3167: bzhengs dang spyan drangs bstims pa dang *//
NG0282:3169: bstan nas dbus su gzhug byas te //
NG0282:3170: mar me thod pa rgyan rnams dgram //
NG0282:3171: phur pa rgyal por dbang bskur bya //
NG0282:3172: de bzhin dkyil 'khor dbus su gzhug / mchod pa'i rdzas dang bskrad pa'i rdzas //
NG0282:3173: gso ba'i rdzas kyang rim pa bzhin //
NG0282:3174: ting 'dzin chen po'i rim pa bzhin //
NG0282:3177: de bzhin las su rung bar bya //
NG0282:3178: som nyi med pa'i rtags byung na //
NG0282:3179: brdungs te las rnams de nyid yin //
NG0282:3180: phab rnams btab la legs par spel //
NG0282:3181: snod du stsal cing bsrung bar bya //
NG0282:3182: du bas bdug cing rgyal pos bsrung *//
NG0282:3184: bzhugs su gsol ba kun kyang bya //
NG0282:3185: til chen me mar gsal ba btang *//
NG0282:3186: rgyan dang cha lugs rab tu bstan //
NG0282:3187: snying po grangs med brjod las 'das //
NG0282:3188: lha la mchod cing srung ma bskul //
NG0282:3189: mchod pa 'bul zhing sbyor bar bya //
NG0282:3190: du ba rlangs pa me 'od dang *//
NG0282:3191: snyan pa'i sgra dang zhim pa'i dri //
NG0282:3192: bar ma chad par byung gyur na //
NG0282:3193: dngos grub las la shis pa yin //
NG0282:3194: ngan na dus drug nyul le bzlog / rta ba'i tshad dang ldan par bya //
NG0282:3195: 'on tang dngos grub yin par nges //
NG0282:3196: dngos grub rdzas rnams bstar byas la //
NG0282:3197: bsrung zhing bskrad de las rnams bya //
NG0282:3198: ye shes lha yi dngos grub dang *//
NG0282:3199: mtshan ma rdzas kyi dngos grub dang *//
NG0282:3200: dbang bskur rim pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:3201: las kyi bya ba kun kyang rdzogs //
NG0282:3202: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3203: sman rigs gcig pa bsgrub pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //    // de nas @#//
NG0282:3204: bcom ldan 'das bdud rtsi so sor sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:3205: rgyu gcig pa dang rkyen gnyis pa //
NG0282:3206: byang chub sems dang sder chags sha / lan tshwa nyid du rkyen du 'gyur //
NG0282:3207: 'byung ba stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
NG0282:3208: bdud rtsi'i lha nyid rnam par gsal //
NG0282:3209: ye shes rdo rje chen po yis //
NG0282:3210: thams cad 'dus pa'i rang bzhin te //
NG0282:3211: 'bru gsum sngags dang lha rnams dang *//
NG0282:3212: bdud rtsi'i sngags kyis rnam par spar //
NG0282:3213: ma grub bar du sngags rnams bzlas //
NG0282:3214: thod pa 'gul dang du ba dang *//
NG0282:3216: me long ye shes dngos grub thob //
NG0282:3218: sul 'greng thod pa mtshan ldan la //
NG0282:3219: rgyu gcig pa dang rkyen gnyis pa //
NG0282:3220: rgyu ni byang chub dri chen la //
NG0282:3221: rmig zlum sha dang brag zhun dang *//
NG0282:3222: rim pa bya ba de bzhin du //
NG0282:3223: de bzhin nyid kyi lha nyid gsal //
NG0282:3224: chos nyid ye shes chen po yis //
NG0282:3225: thams cad 'dus pa dri ma med //
NG0282:3226: sngags gsum de bzhin yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:3227: sgrub pa chen po las kyi mchog / zhim pa'i ngad dang sna tshogs dri //
NG0282:3228: stong pa chen po'i dngos grub thob //
NG0282:3230: sul mang thod pa mtshan ldan la //
NG0282:3231: rgyu gcig pa dang rkyen gnyis pa //
NG0282:3232: mam sa chen po yang dag 'byung */
NG0282:3233: kha brag sha dang dbang po lag / bsgom pa'i lha yang de bzhin te //
NG0282:3234: gsal la rtog pa med pa dang *//
NG0282:3235: mnyam pa'i ye shes chen po yis //
NG0282:3236: thams cad 'byung bas zag pa med //
NG0282:3237: sngags la sbyor ba'i rim pa med //
NG0282:3238: bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu don gyi mchog / 'od dang bar snang 'ja' rnams 'byung *//
NG0282:3239: mnyam pa'i ye shes dngos grub 'byung *//
NG0282:3240: zla gam thod pa mtshan ldan la //
NG0282:3241: rgyu gcig pa dang rkyen gnyis pa //
NG0282:3243: 'dab chags sha dang ram bu dang *//
NG0282:3244: bsgom pas gsal la rtog pa med //
NG0282:3245: rang gsal ba nyid de bzhin no //
NG0282:3246: rtog pa med pa'i ye shes kyis //
NG0282:3247: gsal la gdangs pa pad+ma'i dri //
NG0282:3248: sngags la rim pa'i grangs dang sbyar //
NG0282:3249: bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu dogs pa med //
NG0282:3250: yi dam lha dang mkha' 'gro'i gzugs //
NG0282:3251: so sor rtog pa'i dngos grub thob //
NG0282:3253: rgya gram thod pa mtshan ldan du //
NG0282:3254: rgyu gcig pa dang rkyen gnyis pa //
NG0282:3255: dri chu byang chub sems dpa' dang *//
NG0282:3256: rkang leb sha dang cong zhi dang *//
NG0282:3257: bsgoms pas phrin las thams cad 'grub //
NG0282:3261: sngags las gsum gyis don du sbyar //
NG0282:3262: thams cad 'byung bas re ba skong *//
NG0282:3263: don rnams bstan dang yid du 'ong *//
NG0282:3265: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes thob //
NG0282:3267: stong pa hum dang rdo rje
NG0282:3269: lha nyid bsgom pa'i rim pa yis //
NG0282:3270: gang yin lha la dngos grub 'byung *//
NG0282:3271: rim pa lnga yi 'bras bu ni //
NG0282:3272: rig 'dzin sa la de yis sleb //
NG0282:3273: kun tu bzang po'i byin rlabs yin //
NG0282:3274: de la nyes pa gang yang med //
NG0282:3275: khams gsum nyon mong 'dren pa'i lam //
NG0282:3276: rgyu de rkyen gnyis 'bras bur smin //
NG0282:3277: ye shes lnga yi ngo bo las //
NG0282:3279: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i lha //
NG0282:3280: des na 'bras bu gdon mi za //
NG0282:3281: ye shes chen po'i rang bzhin las //
NG0282:3282: rnam pa lnga yi ngo bo 'byung *//
NG0282:3283: me long ye shes ngo bor gsal //
NG0282:3284: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3285: bdud rtsi lnga bsgrub pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o ///
NG0282:3286: / de nas bcom ldan 'das snang ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:3287: snang ba ye shes rab gsal ba //
NG0282:3288: don dam gsal ba'i ye shes 'byung *//
NG0282:3289: brten pa gsal ba'i chos nyid 'byung *//
NG0282:3290: khams gsum gsal ba'i sgron me 'byung *//
NG0282:3292: thams cad ma bsgribs gsal bar 'byung *//
NG0282:3293: yod med gnyis su med par gsal /
NG0282:3294: khams gsum bde bas gsal ba 'byung *//
NG0282:3295: rang rig ston pa'i sgron me 'byung *//
NG0282:3296: ye shes nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rab tu gsal //
NG0282:3297: snang ba nyi 'od thams cad ston //
NG0282:3298: ma bsgribs gsal ba'i 'od de thams cad ston //
NG0282:3299: nyi ma rang gsal don rnams thams cad ston //
NG0282:3300: dbang po gsal ba'i 'od de don rnams ston / 'od gsal kun dang mthun pa yongs kyis min //
NG0282:3301: rang byung ye shes cir yang gsal ba'i 'od //
NG0282:3302: khams gsum gsal ba'i sgron ma 'byung *//
NG0282:3303: stong pa gsal ba'i sgron ma rab tu gsal //
NG0282:3304: nyi ma'i 'od bzhin thams cad snyoms par 'byung *//
NG0282:3305: 'di ni yang dag gsal ba'i sgron mar gsal //
NG0282:3306: rang byung gsal ba'i dbyings las ma nyams par //
NG0282:3307: stong khams yongs la snyoms pa'i thugs rje 'byung *//
NG0282:3308: yangs pa chen po'i don las ma g.yos par //
NG0282:3309: bde ba chen po'i don rnams ston pa'i mchog / bstan pas gsal ba chen po'i ngang *//
NG0282:3310: thig le chen po cir yang snang ba las //
NG0282:3311: rol pa phyogs med don dam bcud kyi dbyings //
NG0282:3312: dus gsum kun tu 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang *//
NG0282:3313: de nyid rol pa cir yang snang ba'i phyir *//
NG0282:3314: sgron ma gsal ba'i don rnams 'dir bstan pas //
NG0282:3315: rtogs pas gsal ba'i don rnams yongs kyis gsal //
NG0282:3316: bde ba'i don la cir yang gsal ba'i 'od //
NG0282:3317: rang byung rang shar ma bsgribs sa ler gsal //
NG0282:3318: tshul khrims sdom pa kun kyang rab tu bsrung *//
NG0282:3319: 'dzin pas mi 'ching bde ba'i ngang gis gsal //
NG0282:3320: dbang dang dam tshig kun kyang mi spang rab tu bsrungs //
NG0282:3321: lha la mi chags rang bzhin ngang gis stong *//
NG0282:3322: stong pa nyid la mi gnas rol pa cir yang snang *//
NG0282:3323: rol pa rang rgyud mi bzung yan par @#/  / btang *//
NG0282:3324: mkhas pa chen po ston pa'i sgron mar gsal //
NG0282:3325: gsal la 'dzin pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0282:3326: dus gsum kun tu ma bsgribs rab tu gsal //
NG0282:3327: 'byung ba chen po'i dbyings las mi zhen pa //
NG0282:3328: ma yengs don la ci yang sa le mkhyen //
NG0282:3329: gang la bstan pa de las gzhan la bstan du med //
NG0282:3330: nyi ma'i snying po 'gyur ba med pa ltar //
NG0282:3331: rang byung byang chub sems la 'gyur ba med //
NG0282:3332: bde ba'i myu gu bstan pa'i sgron me gsal //
NG0282:3333: don du bstan kyang nges pa de las med //
NG0282:3334: bstan pa nyid la 'di zhes brjod dang bral //
NG0282:3335: bral zhing spang du ci yang med par rtogs //
NG0282:3336: phyogs dang bral zhing phyogs la 'dzin pa med //
NG0282:3337: brdal ba chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos par //
NG0282:3338: gang gi don du de yi bstan par 'byung *//
NG0282:3339: don dam bcud kyi snying po ngang gis gsal //
NG0282:3340: yod pa'i ngo bo cir yang snang ba'i 'od //
NG0282:3341: legs pa'i 'bras bu thob tu med pa'i dbyings //
NG0282:3342: don gyi snying po bde ba 'di las med //
NG0282:3343: bde ba nyid kyang gsal ba'i nyi ma 'dra //
NG0282:3344: dper na chu yi zla ba bzhin te rang bzhin gsal //
NG0282:3345: gang gis bstan pa de yis go bar bstan //
NG0282:3346: de ma rtogs pa'i byang chub snying po ni //
NG0282:3347: gsal ba mi 'dzin rang bzhin 'od kyis gsal //
NG0282:3348: stong pa kun bzang dus gsum 'gyur ba med //
NG0282:3349: rak+sha srin po bde ba'i myu gu brtags //
NG0282:3350: rang rang bag chags brtas pas sdug bsngal 'byung *//
NG0282:3351: mi spang mi 'dor yang dag snying po bral //
NG0282:3352: snying po nyid la 'di zhes bstan du med //
NG0282:3353: snying po nyid kyang don gyis brjod dang bral //
NG0282:3354: snying po 'di la ma 'dus gang yang med //
NG0282:3355: snying po 'di las rol pa cir yang snang *//
NG0282:3356: snying po 'di las sems can sangs rgyas 'byung *//
NG0282:3357: snying po 'di las sku dang ye shes 'byung *//
NG0282:3358: snying po 'di las thams cad mkhyen pa 'byung *//
NG0282:3359: snying po 'di las gsal ba'i ye shes 'byung *//
NG0282:3360: snying po 'di las rigs kyi sangs rgyas 'byung *//
NG0282:3361: snying po 'di las yang dag 'bras bu 'byung *//
NG0282:3362: snying po 'di las bstan pa rgya mtsho 'byung *//
NG0282:3363: snying po 'di las mi bde sna tshogs 'byung *//
NG0282:3364: snying po 'di las sa dang lam du 'byung *//
NG0282:3365: snying po 'di las sa rnams rim par bgrod //
NG0282:3366: snying po ma spangs rang bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:3367: snying po 'di las don rnams yang dag 'byung *//
NG0282:3368: snying po 'di las nges med nges par gzung du med //
NG0282:3369: snying po 'di las byin rlabs thams cad 'byung *//
NG0282:3370: snying po 'di las btsal ba med par gsal //
NG0282:3371: snying po 'di las dbang rnams ma bskur 'thob //
NG0282:3372: snying po 'di las phrin las lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:3373: snying po 'di las zhi khro gnyis su snang *//
NG0282:3374: snying po 'di las bya rtsol med par grub //
NG0282:3375: snying po 'di las snang dang stong par snang *//
NG0282:3376: snying po 'di las byin rlabs shugs kyis 'byung *//
NG0282:3377: snying po 'di las gang bstan thams cad 'grub //
NG0282:3378: snying po 'di las @#/  / gtso dang 'khor du snang *//
NG0282:3379: snying po 'di las btsal du med par 'grub //
NG0282:3380: snying po 'di las dkyil 'khor thams cad 'byung *//
NG0282:3381: snying po 'di las thams cad kun tu gsal //
NG0282:3382: snying po 'di las yongs su brdal ba'i ngang *//
NG0282:3383: snying po 'di las rtsal dang thugs rjer 'brel //
NG0282:3384: snying po 'di las thams cad gzhi dang bral //
NG0282:3385: snying po 'di la bsag pa'i gzhi dang bral //
NG0282:3386: snying po 'di la brten pa'i sa dang bral //
NG0282:3387: snying po 'di la brten pa'i don dang bral //
NG0282:3388: snying po 'di la brjod pa'i tshig dang bral //
NG0282:3389: snying po 'di la lta ba'i yul dang bral //
NG0282:3390: snying po 'di la bsgom pa'i dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3391: snying po 'di la spyod pa'i dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3392: snying po 'di la re ba'i 'bras bu bral //
NG0282:3393: snying po 'di la nga dang bdag tu bral //
NG0282:3394: snying po 'di la brten pa'i dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3395: thams cad gzung ba'i yul med re ba med //
NG0282:3396: snying po nyid kyang bstan pa'i dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3397: spang ba med de rang bzhin ngang gi gsal //
NG0282:3398: gsal ba nyid kyang dmigs pa kun dang bral //
NG0282:3399: gsal ba nyid na 'di zhes bstan du med //
NG0282:3400: med pa ma yin kun gyi snying por gsal //
NG0282:3401: snying po nyid na bde ba chen por gnas //
NG0282:3402: bde bas mi 'dzin rang bzhin cir yang snang *//
NG0282:3403: snang ba kun kyang dmigs pa'i brten pa med //
NG0282:3404: yod dang med pa'i mthar ni cir yang snang *//
NG0282:3405: thams cad nga yin de la nga ma grub //
NG0282:3406: grub pa med de de nyid rab tu bzang *//
NG0282:3407: nga la nga zhes bstan pas rab tu 'khrul //
NG0282:3408: byang chub nyid la 'khrul dang ma 'khrul med //
NG0282:3409: 'khrul pa nyid kyang byang chub chen po'i lam //
NG0282:3410: lam rnams ma bgrod thams cad lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:3411: sa rnams ma sbyangs thams cad grub pa'i sa //
NG0282:3412: sa mchog 'di ni ma btsal lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:3413: sa la brten te sbyang ba'i dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3414: ye shes chen po lhun gyis grub pa'i sa //
NG0282:3415: bde ba chen po rang bzhin rtogs pa'i sa //
NG0282:3416: sa la rnam pa gsum du nges pa med //
NG0282:3417: theg chen sa ni sa gcig kun gyi dus //
NG0282:3418: de nyid ngang las sa rnams lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:3419: thams cad 'byung ba'i sa ste bde ba'i ngang *//
NG0282:3420: lam mchog nyid kyang ma bgrod kun kyang bstan //
NG0282:3421: lam gyi snying po de yis lam rnams thams cad 'grub //
NG0282:3422: lam lnga bgrod pas lam mchog yongs mi thob //
NG0282:3423: bgrod du med pa'i lam chen nga yis bstan //
NG0282:3424: sa dang lam la nges pa de nyid yin //
NG0282:3425: bskal par 'dzom yang de nyid 'dres pa med //
NG0282:3426: g.yeng ba mang po'i don rnams yal bar dor //
NG0282:3427: phyogs su 'dzin cing nga yi rang bzhin can //
NG0282:3428: 'dzin pa nyid kyang sdig pa'i snod dang bral //
NG0282:3429: nyi ma shar ba'i rang bzhin byas pa min //
NG0282:3430: ma byas pa yang min te thams cad de ltar snang *//
NG0282:3431: sku gsung thugs kyang nga ru bstan du med //
NG0282:3432: brjod pa gsum dang bral phyir de bzhin no //
NG0282:3433: brjod pa nyid la brjod pa'i @#/  / dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3434: dang po ma byung tha ma gar mi 'gro //
NG0282:3435: de bzhin dus gsum kun tu 'di la gnas //
NG0282:3436: kun tu bzang po nyid kyang de nyid do //
NG0282:3437: snang ba tsam du rang bzhin gsal ba la //
NG0282:3438: stong pa nyid la tha dad de bzhin 'gyur //
NG0282:3439: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3440: snying po snang bar bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ///
NG0282:3441: / de nas bcom ldan 'das rol pa chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:3442: ye shes bzhi dang rnam pa lnga //
NG0282:3443: me long ye shes kun gyi mchog / thams cad 'di yi ngo bo gsal //
NG0282:3444: stong pa'i ye shes snang ba med //
NG0282:3445: stong pa chen po chos kyi mchog / mnyam nyid ye shes rin po che //
NG0282:3446: snang stong gnyis la khyad par med //
NG0282:3447: so sor rtog pa shes rab yin //
NG0282:3448: rab tu 'byed pa'i ngo bor gnas //
NG0282:3449: bya ba grub pas las rnams ston //
NG0282:3450: thams cad sprul pas stong gsum 'gengs //
NG0282:3451: don rnams ma lus 'grub par byed //
NG0282:3452: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin las //
NG0282:3453: rang bzhin gsal ba'i ye shes te //
NG0282:3454: rigs su phye bas lnga ru bshad //
NG0282:3455: rol pa'i don la khyad par med //
NG0282:3456: gcig ni chos sku don gyis mtshon //
NG0282:3458: gcig ni sprul pa bstan pa bsrung *//
NG0282:3459: don gyi khyad par yang dag pa //
NG0282:3460: lnga pa'i nges par gsal bar 'gyur //
NG0282:3461: don dam ye shes rdzogs pa yis //
NG0282:3462: rol pa chen po'i rigs lngar 'byung *//
NG0282:3463: rdo rje rigs kyi sangs rgyas dang *//
NG0282:3464: grub pa'i 'bras bu gang bstan pa //
NG0282:3465: sa dang lam lnga rab bgrod kyang *//
NG0282:3466: me long ye shes chen po yis //
NG0282:3467: snang ba'i don la cir yang ston //
NG0282:3468: de bzhin rigs kyi sangs rgyas dang *//
NG0282:3469: grub pa'i 'bras bu khyad par can //
NG0282:3470: sa dang lam la ring bas na //
NG0282:3471: stong pa chen po'i dbyings su thim //
NG0282:3472: rin chen rigs kyi sangs rgyas ni //
NG0282:3473: grub pa'i 'bras bu rin chen yang *//
NG0282:3474: gzhi yi don gyis las mi 'grub //
NG0282:3475: skabs kyi 'bras bu rang sar grol //
NG0282:3476: mnyam pa'i ngang du yang dag ston //
NG0282:3477: pad+ma rigs kyi sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0282:3478: bde ba'i 'bras bu don gyis gsal //
NG0282:3479: rim pa grangs la bstan na yang *//
NG0282:3480: bzhi dang lnga ru bstan du med //
NG0282:3481: so sor rtogs pas rtogs pa'i ngang *//
NG0282:3482: las kyi rigs kyi sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0282:3483: grub pa can du bstan pa ste //
NG0282:3484: sa dang lam la bstan par zad //
NG0282:3485: grub pa'i 'bras bu gzhi mi dgos //
NG0282:3486: thams cad gcig pas mi 'byung phyir //
NG0282:3487: bya ba grub pa'i rang bzhin can //
NG0282:3488: sku lnga ye shes rnam lnga yang *//
NG0282:3489: don dam gcig las bstan pa la //
NG0282:3490: de nyid ngo bor 'byung bas na //
NG0282:3491: rig pa can du gang la 'gyur //
NG0282:3492: med par byungaba'i don du yang *//
NG0282:3493: brjod pa'i tshig tsam yang dag min //
NG0282:3494: rang rig gsal ba'i ngo bo las //
NG0282:3495: stong pa'i rig par 'gyur ba med //
NG0282:3496: rig pa thams cad kun gyi gzhi //
NG0282:3497: rig pa sna tshogs byung bas na //
NG0282:3498: rig pa'i ngo bos gzhi rtsa bral / med pa'i
NG0282:3499: rang bzhin gzhi @#/ / rtsa bral / gnyis su
NG0282:3501: chos nyid phur par gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3502: thugs rje phur par gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3503: byang sems phur par gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3504: 'dus byas phur par gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3505: de bzhin nyid du gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3506: lha yi gzhal yas gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3507: lha nyid bsgom par gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3508: spyan dang mchod dang bstod pa dang *//
NG0282:3509: thams cad rang bzhin gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3510: gzhi dang rtsa ba nges gzung med //
NG0282:3511: gzhi rtsa bral ba'i chos nyid ni //
NG0282:3512: cir yang med la cir yang snang *//
NG0282:3513: snang ba nyid kyang gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3514: cir yang med pas ngos gzung med //
NG0282:3515: lha dang lha ru bsgom pa yang *//
NG0282:3516: lha gnyis rang bzhin khyad par med //
NG0282:3517: drang ba'i don du cir yang ston //
NG0282:3518: drang ba nyid du bstan pa ni //
NG0282:3519: nges par brtags pas de bzhin yin //
NG0282:3520: nges pa nyid dang gnyis su med //
NG0282:3521: nges med rang bzhin thams cad ston //
NG0282:3522: spangs pa'i chos nyid thig ltar phra //
NG0282:3523: phra bas dmigs dang bral bar bshad //
NG0282:3524: phra ba'i rang bzhin brtag dka' ba //
NG0282:3525: phra ba'i don nyid cir yang ston //
NG0282:3526: de yis don rnams ston par byed //
NG0282:3527: yang dag nyid du de bstan na //
NG0282:3528: nges pa nyid du 'bras bur bcas //
NG0282:3529: re ba med par don rtogs nas //
NG0282:3530: yang dag bstan pa'i phur pa 'gyur //
NG0282:3531: lha nyid gzhi rtsa ma bral na //
NG0282:3532: yang dag don gyi phur pa min //
NG0282:3533: 'dzin pas bcings pa'i lha nyid ni //
NG0282:3534: gzhi dang rtsa ba bcas pa ste //
NG0282:3535: nges pa can du gyur par na //
NG0282:3536: bya rtsol med pa'i ye shes min //
NG0282:3537: don gyi phur pa gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:3538: nges par phur pa brjod pa bral //
NG0282:3539: snang ba tsam du bstan pa ste //
NG0282:3540: rang rang rgyud du 'dzin pa med //
NG0282:3541: 'dzin pa rang bzhin dngos po ste //
NG0282:3542: de yis bstan pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NG0282:3543: sa dang lam la rim par bstan //
NG0282:3544: rtogs pa med pa'i lha nyid ni //
NG0282:3545: 'bras bu srid pa nyid du brtas //
NG0282:3546: shes pa'i rtog pa rang sar grol //
NG0282:3547: rang grol 'bras bu btsal mi dgos //
NG0282:3548: sangs rgyas sa la rnam pa lnga //
NG0282:3549: rang rig ye shes rtogs pa'i sa //
NG0282:3550: 'dzin pa phyogs su bral ba'i sa //
NG0282:3551: ye shes rgyun mi 'chad pa'i sa //
NG0282:3552: rgyu 'bras gnyis med rtogs pa'i sa //
NG0282:3553: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i sa //
NG0282:3554: lnga yis rang byung sa lnga rtogs //
NG0282:3555: 'byung ba lnga yi rang bzhin la //
NG0282:3556: sangs rgyas zhing khams thams cad rtogs //
NG0282:3557: nam mkha' ston pas rab bstan pa //
NG0282:3558: nges par bstan du med par rtogs //
NG0282:3559: ston pas chu yi don bstan pa //
NG0282:3560: 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyong bar rtogs //
NG0282:3561: ston pas sa yi don bstan pa //
NG0282:3562: 'gro ba tshims byed gsos su rtogs //
NG0282:3563: ston pas me yi don bstan pa //
NG0282:3564: 'khor ba'i rnam rtog bsreg pa dang *//
NG0282:3565: ye shes me chen 'bar ba'i rtags //
NG0282:3566: ston pa lnga yis rab bstan pa //
NG0282:3568: re dogs med par mya ngan 'das //
NG0282:3569: yang dag ston pa'i snying po 'di //
NG0282:3570: chos nyid phur pa'i ngo bo @#/  / ste //
NG0282:3571: sems can drag pos sgrol ba yang *//
NG0282:3572: drag po nyid kyang dmigs dang bral //
NG0282:3573: ye shes me yi khro bo ni //
NG0282:3574: sreg pa'i lha ste 'tshig par byed //
NG0282:3575: khams gsum 'khru byed ye shes chu //
NG0282:3577: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:3578: rol pa chen po'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0282:3579: / de nas bcom ldan 'das rab tu+u byams pa
NG0282:3580: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NG0282:3581: / rdo rje phur pa'i chos nyid las //
NG0282:3582: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa yis //
NG0282:3583: dus gsum bde gshegs dgongs pa 'dus //
NG0282:3584: shes pa'i khyad par bsam 'das pa //
NG0282:3585: rol pa'i theg pa bsam las 'das //
NG0282:3586: yin dang ma yin brtag dka' bas //
