NG0282:4336: mu khyud thod pa'i brtsig pa bya //
NG0282:4337: rin po che yi 'od dang bcas //
NG0282:4338: dbye ba'i rdzas dang 'gugs pa'i rdzas //
NG0282:4339: bcing ba'i rdzas dang smyo ba'i rdzas //
NG0282:4340: bsgral ba'i rdzas dang bstab pa'i rdzas //
NG0282:4341: rdzas drug drag po las kyi rdzas //
NG0282:4342: seng ldeng phur bu sor bcu gnyis //
NG0282:4343: nyung dkar nyid du bcas pa dang *//
NG0282:4344: dar gyi cod pan lnga btag pa //
NG0282:4345: gtso bo nyid la de bzhin bsham //
NG0282:4346: lha drug phur bu thugs kyi mchog / lha ru dbang sdud las la 'gyed //
NG0282:4347: seng ldeng phur bu sor brgyad ni //
NG0282:4348: rdzu 'phrul ston cing nus pa can //
NG0282:4349: de yis lha dbral las rnams byed /  / bya rgod gshog phur zhi ba ste //
NG0282:4350: gdug pa klu rnams zhi bar byed //
NG0282:4351: gser ram ser po rgyas pa ste //
NG0282:4352: tshe dang dbang thang rgyas par byed //
NG0282:4353: zangs sam ljon dmar mchog phur yang */
NG0282:4354: khams gsum dbang du sdud pas na //
NG0282:4355: lcags sam ljon shing sgrol ma'i rdzas //
NG0282:4356: tsan+dan rgya shug gzi byin myur du sdud pa'i rdzas //
NG0282:4357: rdzas drug de bzhin las rnams bya //
NG0282:4358: bar chad bsal ba'i las rnams bya //
NG0282:4359: dang po stong pa'i rang bzhin las //
NG0282:4360: hum dang rdo rje sngags kyis bskyed //
NG0282:4361: snyan gsan spyan drangs bstim par bya //
NG0282:4362: mchod pa bstod pa ma lus kun //
NG0282:4363: yang dag nyid du de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:4364: dbus su seng ldeng phur pa dgod //
NG0282:4365: steng du 'dul ba nam mkha' ste //
NG0282:4366: steng la sogs pa phur bu drug / rim pa bzhin du dgod par bya //
NG0282:4367: steng du gu gul rdzas rnams gzhag / shar du
NG0282:4368: lcags kyu nyung dkar bzhag / lho ru zhags pa
NG0282:4369: sngon dmar gzhag / nub tu dug rdzas mang du
NG0282:4370: gzhag / byang du ral gri tho ba gzhag /
NG0282:4371: 'og tu ming dang rus su bcas //
NG0282:4372: ting 'dzin rim pa bsgom pas ste //
NG0282:4374: ma gzhag / steng du snying sna bzhi la bya //
NG0282:4375: shar du klu sman de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4376: lho ru dkar po lnga la bya //
NG0282:4377: nub tu ra dang khyi la bya //
NG0282:4378: byang du nag po gsum la bya //
NG0282:4379: 'og tu ra dmar gtor ma bya //
NG0282:4380: ting 'dzin dpal du bsgom byas nas //
NG0282:4381: rang rang sngags kyis 'khor rnams bskyed //
NG0282:4382: snyan gsan spyan drang bstim pa dang *//
NG0282:4383: mchod pa 'bul dang dngos grub dang *//
NG0282:4384: sbyor ba'i bar du sgrol ba rnams //
NG0282:4385: bstab pa chen po de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4386: bsnyen pa ye shes lha nyid la //
NG0282:4387: gdug pa drug gi sngags bzlas pa //
NG0282:4388: bstod pa de bzhin rim pas 'byung *//
NG0282:4389: tshogs pa sbyor ba de bzhin te //
NG0282:4390: pho nya las bzhi'i phur pa gdang *//
NG0282:4391: de bzhin bsnyen pa'i las rnams bya //
NG0282:4392: sa ya drug 'bum mang du bskyal //
NG0282:4394: mtshan ma tsam du 'byung ba dang *//
NG0282:4395: 'od dang me dang du ba dang *//
NG0282:4396: mi ring nam mkha' gang ba dang *//
NG0282:4397: rta dang khyi dang sbrul dang bya //
NG0282:4398: rtags la bab pa rab tu brtag / nges par gdeng du gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:4399: bsgrub pa'i las ni shes par bya //
NG0282:4400: lha dang rdzas kyi bye brag dang *//
NG0282:4401: sngags dang bskul ba de bzhin te //
NG0282:4402: gtso bo gsal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NG0282:4403: 'khor rnams gsal bar gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:4404: thams cad sngags la rab tu 'dus //
NG0282:4405: sngags rnams 'grub pa rab tu gces //
NG0282:4406: ye shes lnga yi sngags rnams la //
NG0282:4407: dregs pa'i sngags nyid rab tu gdags //
NG0282:4408: rkyang par mi bya dril ba dang *//
NG0282:4410: thun gyi phur pa drug gam gcig / gcig la rdzas drug rang rang brab //
NG0282:4411: gcig la rdzas rnams dril ba ste /
NG0282:4412: khrag dang snying du bcas pa la //
NG0282:4413: so sor rang rang dam rdzas brab //
NG0282:4414: gang yin nyams pa bsgral bar bya //
NG0282:4415: thun nyid khol dang lud pa dang *//
NG0282:4416: mang ba tsam du gyur pa na //
NG0282:4417: nyung dkar nyung nag skye tshe dang *//
NG0282:4418: d+ha ru ra yi rtsa ba yis //
NG0282:4419: nyin dang mtshan du dus med par //
NG0282:4420: yang nas yang du bab par bya //
NG0282:4421: de yis thun kyang rab tu khol //
NG0282:4422: nan du dkar po sngags la sbyar //
NG0282:4423: nag po de bzhin rab tu mnan //
NG0282:4424: rtags de brtan par byung ba dang *//
NG0282:4425: drag po'i las la sbyar bar bya //
NG0282:4426: bdud kyi nyi ma bkra mi shis //
NG0282:4427: ngan pa'i las rnams bya bar 'byung *//
NG0282:4428: nyi nag mar gyi do dag gam //
NG0282:4430: dur du 'jug dang rgyu ba dang *//
NG0282:4431: mngon du byung dang khugs pa dang *//
NG0282:4432: drag po'i bsam pa skyes pa dang *//
NG0282:4433: me yi 'od du byung ba na //
NG0282:4434: de yis las nyid myur bar 'grub //
NG0282:4435: klong du bstan pa'i las bya ste //
NG0282:4436: spyir yang 'di nyid klong drug ste //
NG0282:4437: gtso bo pho nya gong bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:4438: sgrol ba gnas su bcas pas gdab //
NG0282:4439: thun kyang rab tu de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4440: 'khor lo klong drug rang rang ste //
NG0282:4441: dang po bral ba'i klong nyid la //
NG0282:4442: rang gis klong dang sngags su bcas //
NG0282:4445: thun kyang de bzhin shes par bya //
NG0282:4446: phyi ma lnga yang de bzhin te //
NG0282:4447: rang rang pho nya sngags rnams dang *//
NG0282:4448: rang rang thun dang rdzas rnams dang *//
NG0282:4449: gsum du sbrel ba'i sngags nyid la //
NG0282:4450: phur pa rang rang de bzhin gdab //
NG0282:4451: gtso bos snying la de bzhin te //
NG0282:4452: 'khor rnams yan lag rnams la gdab //
NG0282:4453: yang na snying la de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:4454: mtshon dang dug kyang de bzhin te /  / gdung ba drag pos btab pa dang *//
NG0282:4455: byang chub sems dpa' rab bstan te //
NG0282:4456: byad dang me dang gnan pa dang *//
NG0282:4457: tshe bstim rim pa sngags kyi bya //
NG0282:4458: las rnams ma lus rdzogs par 'gyur //
NG0282:4459: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4460: drag po'i las bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o
NG0282:4461: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gdug pa lha
NG0282:4462: dang dbye ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:4463: te / drag po las kyi don bsnyan pa //
NG0282:4464: dbye ba'i las rnams ma byas na //
NG0282:4465: gdug pa'i las rnams rdugs par 'gyur //
NG0282:4466: dur khrod dmar la mtho ba la //
NG0282:4467: shar gyi phyogs su sgo bstan pa //
NG0282:4468: nyi ma'i zer ma nang du 'char //
NG0282:4469: de lta'i gnas dang ldan pa dang *//
NG0282:4470: man+dal mda' gang byas nas su //
NG0282:4471: mi yi de bzhin rus pas gdab //
NG0282:4472: dmar chen khrag gnyis rab tu byug / gru gsum zla gam mu khyud bri //
NG0282:4473: mu khyud dur khrod brtsig pa la //
NG0282:4474: shar du bstan pa'i sgo gnas pa'o //
NG0282:4475: de yi phyi rim zlum po la //
NG0282:4476: dmar po byas te gzugs kyang bri //
NG0282:4477: dbus su dpal gyi gtor ma ste //
NG0282:4478: khyad par nyid du gyur pa'o //
NG0282:4479: shar gyi mu ran zlum po la //
NG0282:4480: 'jig rten dregs pa'i gtor ma gzhag / rten du bcas pa ma lus kun //
NG0282:4481: yang dag nyid du brjod par bya //
NG0282:4482: dbus su bsnyen pa'i phur pa la //
NG0282:4483: mthing nag dar gyi cod pan gdags //
NG0282:4484: shar du seng ldeng phur pa la //
NG0282:4485: snying po bris la yang dag dgod //
NG0282:4486: dbus su snying chen ma nyams gzhag / shar du+u
NG0282:4487: ra snying de bzhin gzhag / dbus su ming byang
NG0282:4488: rus su bcug / shar du ra yi snying khrag
NG0282:4489: gam // yang na ra sog g.yas pa la //
NG0282:4490: ming byang bris la de bzhin gzhag / yang na
NG0282:4491: ra mgor ming byang bcug / rtsang gis btsug la
NG0282:4492: sngo dmar bcings // dregs pa'i snying po de bzhin bri //
NG0282:4493: rim pas bsnyen pa de bzhin du //
NG0282:4495: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas su //
NG0282:4496: dbus su bsnyen pa'i phur pa dgod //
NG0282:4497: shar sgor sras mchog phur pa dgod //
NG0282:4498: phyi rol dregs pa'i rdzas rnams dgod //
NG0282:4499: bsgom pa'i rim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:4500: spyan drangs bstim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:4501: bsnyen pa ye shes lha la dbul //
NG0282:4503: bstod cing bskul te las rnams bcol //
NG0282:4504: hum mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NG0282:4505: yab gcig rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NG0282:4506: sku ni ri rab nyi zla'i gzugs //
NG0282:4507: rngam pa chen po'i tshems brdar @#//
NG0282:4509: gdug pa can rnams zhabs kyis gnon //
NG0282:4510: phyag gi phur pas nyon mongs spyod //
NG0282:4511: zhabs bzhi rdzu 'phrul bzhi dang ldan //
NG0282:4512: spyan mig gru gsum dug gsum 'dul //
NG0282:4513: ya mtshan chen po 'phrul gyi lha //
NG0282:4514: gdug pa 'dul ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:4515: nyon mongs 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:4516: me dpung chen po'i 'od la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0282:4517: hum thugs kyi sprul pa cir yang ston //
NG0282:4518: ya mtshan chen po lha yi lha //
NG0282:4519: khams gsum gdug pa 'dul ba'i dpal //
NG0282:4520: stong gsum rngams pa drag pa'i sgra //
NG0282:4521: ye shes lha yi sprul pa ste //
NG0282:4522: ma bskul dbyings nas bzhengs pa'i lha //
NG0282:4523: mthing ga 'jigs pa'i sku mdog la //
NG0282:4524: nyon mongs 'joms pa'i phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4525: rang rtags 'brel pa'i gu gul dang *//
NG0282:4526: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa 'dzin //
NG0282:4527: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NG0282:4528: smad ni zur gsum dbal dang ldan //
NG0282:4530: thugs dam chen po'i dbyings nas bskul //
NG0282:4532: las rnams ma lus 'grub pa dang //
NG0282:4533: lha yi las byas dregs pa 'dul //
NG0282:4534: dregs pa sngags kyi sbyor ba yis //
NG0282:4535: ran dang mdzes par rab sbyar la //
NG0282:4536: mchod pa'i dus su phur pa gdab //
NG0282:4537: dum bur gtum cing mchod par dbul //
NG0282:4538: bstod cing bskul ba yang nas yang *//
NG0282:4539: thun rnams ra thod nang du sbyar //
NG0282:4540: snying dang khrag dang de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:4541: de nyid las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:4542: gdab pa'i las nyid 'di lta ste //
NG0282:4543: gu gul du bas bdug byas te //
NG0282:4544: dbral ba'i sngags dang tshig tu bcas //
NG0282:4545: yang nas yang du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4546: pho nya las rnams de bzhin te //
NG0282:4547: gdab pa'i sngags gnyis snying la gdab //
NG0282:4548: thun dang de bzhin 'dzom par byas //
NG0282:4549: mtshon dang dug dang brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:4550: gdab dang byang sems sngags kyis bya //
NG0282:4551: me la bsregs te phye ma dang *//
NG0282:4552: sol bas g.yogs pa'i ming byang rnams //
NG0282:4553: sngon dmar dag gis rab dkris la //
NG0282:4554: ra yi thod pa'i nang du gzhug / la btsas dag la rab tu sba //
NG0282:4555: gtor ma tshe bstim bkra shis dang *//
NG0282:4556: de bzhin las rdzogs rdzogs par bya /
NG0282:4557: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4558: lha dang dbral ba'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o //
NG0282:4559: // de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po 'gugs pa'i
NG0282:4560: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:4561: dur khrod chen po gangs dang shel lta bu //
NG0282:4562: rgyal po'i pho brang gnas dag dang *//
NG0282:4563: de bzhin mchod pa'i sa yod par //
NG0282:4564: sgo yi phyogs kyang shar du bltas //
NG0282:4565: rta dang bya yi gzugs yod par //
NG0282:4566: man+dal mda' gang byas nas su //
NG0282:4567: dkar po gsum gyi khrag gis byugs //
NG0282:4568: gru gsum zla gam mu khyud bri //
NG0282:4569: mu khyud de bzhin bstan pa la //
NG0282:4570: dkar po'i mu ran yang gcig bsnan //
NG0282:4571: dbus su dpal gyi snying po bri //
NG0282:4572: shar du 'gugs pa'i snying po bri //
NG0282:4575: sras mchog bya rgod gshog thur la //
NG0282:4576: dar gyi cod pan de bzhin gdags //
NG0282:4577: bar chad bsal ba'i las byas la //
NG0282:4578: dbus su bsnyen pa'i phur pa la //
NG0282:4579: gtso bo'i phur pa dbus su dgod //
NG0282:4580: shar gyi phur pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4581: dbus su dpal gyi gtor ma ni //
NG0282:4582: khyad par rmad du byung bar bya //
NG0282:4583: gdug pa'i gtor ma snying sna gsum //
NG0282:4584: bse phor bshams te shar du gzhag / rten yang
NG0282:4585: de bzhin shar du gzhag / ming rus dbus dang
NG0282:4586: shar du gzhag / drag po'i rtsang gis bskor bar
NG0282:4587: bya // ting 'dzin rim pa bstan par bya //
NG0282:4588: gzhal yas gdan dang bcas pa ru //
NG0282:4589: dbus su gtso bo rab bskyed la //
NG0282:4590: shar du 'gugs pa'i lha mchog bskyed //
NG0282:4591: spyan drang rim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:4592: bstim dang mchod pa ma lus bya //
NG0282:4593: ye shes lha la bsnyen pa bya //
NG0282:4594: shar gyi de bzhin shes par gyis //
NG0282:4595: bskul zhing bstod pa 'di lta ste //
NG0282:4596: hum gdug pa 'dul ba drag po'i sku //
NG0282:4597: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug la //
NG0282:4598: smad ni zur gsum dpal dang ldan //
NG0282:4599: dkar ba'i zhal la drag po'i dbyibs //
NG0282:4600: gdug pa 'dul ba'i phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4601: lcags kyu'i stangs stabs phyag rgya can //
NG0282:4602: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4604: mang du sprul cing las la gus //
NG0282:4605: gang yin 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig / snying khrag rnam gsum sbreng byed cing *//
NG0282:4606: mchod pa'i dus su bkug cing bstim / bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams 'di lta ste //
NG0282:4608: dngos su byung ngam nyams su byung *//
NG0282:4609: de ni bsnyen pa'i rtags su bstan //
NG0282:4610: ran dang mdzes pa'i lha sngags la //
NG0282:4611: drag po'i sngags kyi gnad du bstan //
NG0282:4612: nyin dang mtshan du rab bstan nas //
NG0282:4613: lha la mchod cing dregs pa bskul //
NG0282:4614: klu yis bzung ba'i thod pa ru //
NG0282:4615: snying po bri zhing thum po bya //
NG0282:4616: gdug pa sbrul gyi snying la gzhug / sbal pa pho mo'i gzugs bris la //
NG0282:4617: dkar po'i snying dang sbal pa dang */
NG0282:4618: khrag dang bsres pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4619: bsnol mtshams brtan pa rab tu gces //
NG0282:4620: thun sngags bzlas shing de la brab //
NG0282:4621: thun de las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:4622: gdug pa dngos su ston pa dang *//
NG0282:4624: yang nas yang du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4625: drag po bsgral ba'i ngo bo ni //
NG0282:4626: lan gsum mnan te pho nyas dgug / dbang po mngon gsum gsal bar 'gyur //
NG0282:4627: gdab pa rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NG0282:4628: thun yang de bzhin yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:4629: mtshon la sogs pa de bzhin 'byung *//
NG0282:4630: tha ma bsreg ste gnan pa bya //
NG0282:4631: 'phang dang bsregs pa'i lhag ma de //
NG0282:4632: bsam pa nyid kyis gsos byas la //
NG0282:4633: byang du kha bltas 'gram du mnan //
NG0282:4635: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4636: drag po 'gugs pa'i le'u ste bcu dgu @#//
NG0282:4637: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po
NG0282:4638: bcing ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NG0282:4639: / dur khrod sngo la 'od chags su //
NG0282:4640: klu yi pho brang yod pa ru //
NG0282:4641: man+dal de bzhin yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:4642: gser ram ser po'i phur pa la //
NG0282:4643: dar yi cod pan de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4644: tsham rngams drag pos bgegs bskrad la //
NG0282:4645: 'god pa de bzhin yang dag bstan //
NG0282:4646: gtor ma dbus dang shar du dgod //
NG0282:4647: shar du dgod pa'i gtor ma la //
NG0282:4648: rtsi sman sna tshogs dgod par bya //
NG0282:4649: rten yang rab tu de bzhin gzhag / ming byang rtsang dang bcas pa yang *//
NG0282:4650: de bzhin brten te rab tu dgod //
NG0282:4651: ting 'dzin rim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:4652: gtso dang 'khor yang de bzhin bskyed //
NG0282:4653: spyan drang rim pa grangs dang sbyar //
NG0282:4654: mchod pa bsnyen pa bstod pa dang *//
NG0282:4655: bsnyen pa ye shes lha la 'bul //
NG0282:4656: ran pa nyid du de bzhin sbyar //
NG0282:4657: hum gdug pa 'dul ba drag po'i sku //
NG0282:4658: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NG0282:4659: smad ni zur gsum dbal dang ldan //
NG0282:4660: sngo ba'i zhal ni 'gyur ba med //
NG0282:4661: gdug pa 'dul ba'i phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4662: zhags pa rang rtags phyag rgya can //
NG0282:4663: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4664: gdug pa shar gyi 'khor lo bcas //
NG0282:4665: sprul pa gang yin nyams pa 'ching *//
NG0282:4666: gang yin bcing ba'i las mdzod cig / dam rdzas nyid kyis de bzhin mchod //
NG0282:4667: mchod pa'i dus su rab tu 'ching bar bstan //
NG0282:4668: bsnyen pa'i rtags ni 'di lta ste //
NG0282:4669: sbrul dang sbal pa la sogs pa //
NG0282:4670: dngos su byung ba ma nyams su byung *//
NG0282:4671: sngon du byung ba'i 'od bzhin du //
NG0282:4672: bsnyen pa'i rtags ni de ltar 'byung *//
NG0282:4673: lha sngags bstan pas de nyid tsam //
NG0282:4674: drag po'i sngags la nan tan bya //
NG0282:4675: nyin dang mtshan du grangs med bzlas //
NG0282:4676: bstod dang bskul pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4677: dkar po gsum gyi thod pa ru //
NG0282:4678: sngags bris thun gyi rdzas rnams bsham //
NG0282:4679: dkar po gsum gyi snying yang gzhug / gzugs bris khrag tu de bzhin bcas //
NG0282:4680: don gyi sbyar ba de bzhin bya //

NG0282:4682: de nyid las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:4683: cha byad ston cing thun nyid khol //

NG0282:4686: yang dang yang du rab tu bsdam //
NG0282:4687: yan lag dngos su bcings par 'gyur //
NG0282:4688: gdab pa'i thun yang de bzhin bstan //
NG0282:4689: las rnams ma lus rdzogs par bya //
NG0282:4690: sreg dang 'phang ba de bzhin du //
NG0282:4691: yang gcig mnan te pho brang sba //
NG0282:4692: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4693: drag po bcings pa'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NG0282:4694: // de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po smyo ba'i
NG0282:4695: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:4696: dur khrod chen po zad zed can //
NG0282:4698: the'u rang gnas pa'i sa yod par //
NG0282:4699: sgo ni shar lho mtshams su bltas //
NG0282:4702: rnam pa gsum gyis rab tu byug / gru gsum de bzhin rim pas bya //
NG0282:4703: ser po mu ran yang gcig bsnan //
NG0282:4704: snying po bri ba de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4705: shar du smyo ba'i snying po bri *//
NG0282:4706: bsnyen phur smyo ba'i snying po yang */  / dar gyi cod pan de bzhin gdags //
NG0282:4707: nyes pa med phyir bsrung ba bya //
NG0282:4708: gtso 'khor phur pa byin brlabs la //
NG0282:4709: rang rang gnas su de bzhin dgod //
NG0282:4710: dpal gyi gtor ma khyad par can //
NG0282:4711: snying sna gsum la de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4712: dkar po sna dmar thod par bya //
NG0282:4713: rten yang de bzhin yang dag gzhag / rtsang gis de bzhin rab tu bskor //
NG0282:4714: ting 'dzin rim pa'i khyad par las //
NG0282:4715: dur khrod gzhal yas gdan yang bcas //
NG0282:4716: dbus dang shar du lha nyid bskyed //
NG0282:4717: rim pa bzhin du yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:4718: bstim dang mchod pa ma lus bya //
NG0282:4719: bsnyen pa rdzogs pa rab tu gces //
NG0282:4720: rim pa bzhin du de ltar bya //
NG0282:4721: bskul pa dang ni bstod pa bya //
NG0282:4722: hum gdug pa 'dul ba drag po'i sku //
NG0282:4723: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug la //
NG0282:4724: smad ni zur gsum dpal dang ldan //
NG0282:4725: dmar pa'i zhal la dbang du sdud //
NG0282:4726: gdug pa 'dul ba phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4727: drag po'i dug gtor rang rtags can /
NG0282:4728: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4729: gdug pa yam shud 'khor dang bcas //
NG0282:4730: sprul pas nyams pa smyo bar mdzod //
NG0282:4731: mchod pa 'bul ba'i las nyid bya //
NG0282:4732: mchod pa'i dus su smyo ru gzhug / bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams rab tu 'byung *//
NG0282:4733: dkar ser 'od kyi rnam pa dang *//
NG0282:4734: btsun pa ban+de bong bu dang *//
NG0282:4735: de ltar rtags rnams byung ba dang *//
NG0282:4736: bsnyen sngags sgrub sngags sha thang dbye //
NG0282:4737: drag po nyid du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4738: mang po'i byin rlab shugs kyis 'byung *//
NG0282:4739: bstod cing bskul ba'i las nyid bya //
NG0282:4740: bong bu dag gi thod pa ru //
NG0282:4741: sngags bris thun rnams rab tu blug / ming dang khrag tu bcas pa bya //
NG0282:4742: rgyu ba'i dus su yang dag bya //
NG0282:4743: nan tan drag po'i thun la bya //
NG0282:4744: las rnams 'grub par gdon mi za //
NG0282:4745: gzugs ston rtags gnyis rab tu 'byung *//
NG0282:4746: smyo ba drag po'i las bya ste //
NG0282:4747: mang du de bzhin nan tan bya //
NG0282:4748: dbang po nyams pas smyo bar 'gyur //
NG0282:4749: gdab ste las ni mtha' ru dbyung *//
NG0282:4750: 'phang dang bsreg pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:4751: dug gis brdeg cing sa der mnan //
NG0282:4752: tshe dang bkra shis de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4753: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4754: drag po smyo ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o ///
NG0282:4755: / de nas bcom ldan 'das sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:4756: dur khrod brag nag nub sgo can //
NG0282:4757: man+dal mda' gang byas nas su //
NG0282:4758: nag po gsum gyi khrag gis byug / rim pa bzhin du bris pa dang *//
NG0282:4759: nag po'i mu ran yang gcig mnan //
NG0282:4760: rang rang gnas su snying po bri //
NG0282:4761: bsnyen phur sgrol ba'i phur pa yang *//
NG0282:4762: cod pan rigs dang yang dag sbyar //
NG0282:4763: bskrad pa'i las rnams de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4766: gang yin gnas su de bzhin dgod //
NG0282:4767: rnam gnyis gtor ma de bzhin du //
NG0282:4768: nag po'i thod par de bzhin bsham //
NG0282:4769: bdud lug nag po rten du bcas //
NG0282:4770: dmigs pa'i rten du de bzhin te //
NG0282:4771: rim pas bskor te de nyid dngos //
NG0282:4772: ting 'dzin gsal ba'i khyad par las //
NG0282:4773: gru gsum e yi dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0282:4774: yab yum dbus dang gdug pa shar //
NG0282:4775: spyan drang byon dang bstim pa dang *//
NG0282:4776: lha la 'bul zhing shags kyis dbye //
NG0282:4777: bskul bas las rnams byed par 'gyur //
NG0282:4778: hum gdug pa 'dul ba drag po'i sku //
NG0282:4779: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug la //
NG0282:4780: smad ni zur gsum dbal dang ldan //
NG0282:4781: gnag pa'i zhal la khro gnyer can //
NG0282:4782: gdug pa 'dul ba phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4783: tho ba phur pa rang rtags can /
NG0282:4784: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4786: bdud kyi sprul pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:4787: gang yin sgrol pa'i las rnams mdzod //
NG0282:4788: nag po gsum gyi khrag gis mchod //
NG0282:4789: mchod pa'i dus su bsgral bar bya //
NG0282:4790: bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams rab tu 'byung *//
NG0282:4791: sgra dang nag po'i 'od dag dang *//
NG0282:4794: bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams rab tu gces //
NG0282:4795: lha dang dregs pa sgrol ba'i sngags //
NG0282:4796: gang yin sha thang dbye bar bya //
NG0282:4797: drag po nyid du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4798: smyo ba med par las rnams bya //
NG0282:4799: mchod cing drag pos rab tu bskul //
NG0282:4800: bdud rta nag po'i thod pa ru //
NG0282:4801: sngags dang thun sngags rab tu bcas //
NG0282:4802: gang yin rgyu dus dag tu bzlas //
NG0282:4803: drag po thugs nyid las kyi mchog / mang du 'byung zhing dngos su ston //
NG0282:4804: gang yin bsgral ba las kyi mchog / gdab dang las rnams rdzogs par bya //
NG0282:4805: lam po che yi rgya gram mnan //
NG0282:4806: bkra shis tshe yi las rnams bya //
NG0282:4807: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4808: drag po bsgral ba'i le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o
NG0282:4809: // // de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po bstab
NG0282:4810: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:4811: dur khrod shing rtsi chu mig can //
NG0282:4812: klu shing sna dgu yod pa'i sar //
NG0282:4813: sa yang ljang sngon de bzhin 'byung *//
NG0282:4814: man+dal mda' gang gru bzhi la //
NG0282:4815: nag po bzhin du rim pas bri //
NG0282:4816: ljang gu'i mu ran yang gcig bsnan //
NG0282:4817: snying po mnan pa de bzhin bri //
NG0282:4818: rnam pa gnyis kyi phur pa yang *//
NG0282:4819: cod pan gdags pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4820: srung ba'i mtshams kyis rab tu bsrung *//
NG0282:4821: rnam pa gnyis su byin brlab bya //
NG0282:4822: gnas gnyis nyid du de bzhin dgod //
NG0282:4823: thun rdzas rnam gnyis de bzhin bsham //
NG0282:4824: rus sbal thod par yang dag bya //
NG0282:4825: chu lug sngo bkra rten du bcas //
NG0282:4826: rus dang ming yang de bzhin bri //
NG0282:4827: rim pa grangs su de bzhin bstan //
NG0282:4828: ting 'dzin sgrol ba'i grangs dang sbyor //
NG0282:4831: lha gnyis rang rang gnas su bsgom //
NG0282:4832: bzhengs dang spyan drang bstim mchod dang *//
NG0282:4833: bskul ba nyid du lha nyid gsal //
NG0282:4834: hum gdug pa 'dul ba drag po'i sku //
NG0282:4835: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug la //
NG0282:4836: smad ni zur gsum dbal dang ldan //
NG0282:4837: ljang ba'i zhal la phrin las rdzogs //
NG0282:4838: gdug pa 'dul ba phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4839: rang rtags gang yin phur pa bsnams /
NG0282:4840: khams gsum gdar gcod phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:4842: btsan gyi sprul pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0282:4843: gang yin bstab pa'i las rnams mdzod //
NG0282:4844: gang yin snying khrag dag gi mchod //
NG0282:4845: mchod pa'i dus su bstab pa bya //
NG0282:4846: bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams 'byung ba yang *//
NG0282:4848: rta dang ra dang sha ba dang *//
NG0282:4849: glang bu+u la sogs dngos sam nyams //
NG0282:4850: bsnyen pa'i rtags rnams rab tu gces //
NG0282:4851: lha dang dregs pa stob pa'i sngags //
NG0282:4852: de nyid bstan par go bar bya //
NG0282:4853: drag po nyid du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4854: byin rlabs nus pa mang bas 'byung *//
NG0282:4855: bstod cing bskul ba'i las rnams bya //
NG0282:4856: btsan rta dmar po'i thod pa ru //
NG0282:4857: sngags bris thun rnams rab tu bsham //
NG0282:4858: snying dang khrag tu bcas pa blugs //
NG0282:4859: gang yin rgyu ba'i dus su sbyar //
NG0282:4860: drag po nan tan thun la bya //
NG0282:4862: dngos sam nyams sam mang ba dang *//
NG0282:4863: khol pa dag kyang rab tu bzang *//
NG0282:4864: bstab pa drag po las bya'i phyir //
NG0282:4865: yang nas yang du de bzhin bya //
NG0282:4866: rang dbang med de stob par 'gyur //
NG0282:4867: gdab pa'i las nyid 'di lta ste //
NG0282:4868: snying dang yan lag de bzhin gdab //
NG0282:4869: mtshon dang dug dang brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:4870: bstab pa byas te sreg dang 'phang *//
NG0282:4871: tshe bstim bkra shis de ltar bya //
NG0282:4872: ma lus rdzogs pa'i las kyi mchog / bsnyen pa ye shes lha la 'bul //
NG0282:4873: bsgrub pa dregs pa drug la 'bul //
NG0282:4874: mchod pa'i dus su las drug 'byung *//
NG0282:4875: bri ba de bzhin dbyings su mthun //
NG0282:4876: bsags pa'i rdzas drug rang rang ste //
NG0282:4877: phur pa drug yang de bzhin du //
NG0282:4878: thod pa drug yang rab tu bstan //
NG0282:4879: rtags drug mi mthun rang rang ste //
NG0282:4880: bstod pa gcig la bskul pa drug / lha sngags
NG0282:4881: gcig la gcig par drug / lha yi gcig la
NG0282:4882: las sna drug / thun yang de bzhin shes par
NG0282:4883: bya / rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:4884: drag po bstab pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi
NG0282:4885: shu gsum pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das
NG0282:4886: drag sngags bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NG0282:4887: zhugs te // bstan pa gnyan por 'tshe byed dang *//
NG0282:4888: sgrol ba'i zhing du gyur pa la //
NG0282:4889: drag po dregs pa'i man ngag bstan //
NG0282:4890: dregs pa'i rgyal po bco lnga la //
NG0282:4891: thod pa mtshan ldan sna gnyis su //
NG0282:4892: snying khrag lnga yi gtor ma bya //
NG0282:4893: yang na thod pa bco lnga ste //
NG0282:4894: nag po lnga la dkar po lnga //
NG0282:4895: dmar dang sngo dang zhur ba dang *//
NG0282:4898: de bzhin snying khrag gtor ma bya //
NG0282:4899: yang na thod pa gcig tu bya //
NG0282:4900: snying sna khrag sna mang du brdar //
NG0282:4901: mtshan ma ngan pa'i thod pa la //
NG0282:4902: med du mi rung snying po bri //
NG0282:4903: gnyis su bcad pa'i dum bu la //
NG0282:4904: lus kyi phyogs su bdud po bri //
NG0282:4905: spyi bor gdug pa 'khor lo bri //
NG0282:4906: drug dang brgyad du+u rab skor la //
NG0282:4907: drag sngags drug la bri bar bya //
NG0282:4908: brgyad la dregs pa'i snying po bri //
NG0282:4909: mu khyud mu bran las sngags bri //
NG0282:4910: de bzhin phyi mar rtsa sngags bri //
NG0282:4911: rtsibs mchan rnams la ming byang bri //
NG0282:4912: lus kyi phyogs su bdud pho bri /
NG0282:4913: kha gdangs mche ba gtsigs pa bri //
NG0282:4914: bar du ming byang gzhug par bya //
NG0282:4915: thod pa ngan pa'i mtshan ldan la //
NG0282:4916: khrag sna mang du blugs byas la //
NG0282:4917: thun du 'phang ba'i rdzas du bya //
NG0282:4918: gru gsum khru gang brkos pa la //
NG0282:4919: de rnams bcug ste kha bcad la //
NG0282:4920: rdo rje rgya gram ldong ros kyis //
NG0282:4921: g.yam pa dag la bri ba dang *//
NG0282:4922: mi mngon legs par gcad par bya //
NG0282:4923: nyung dkar nyung nag ske tshe dang *//
NG0282:4924: dug dang snying sna'i phye ma la //
NG0282:4925: skyes pa dar ma'i mchog phur dang *//
NG0282:4926: sa ser dngos po'i phye ma rnams //
NG0282:4927: thun gyi rdzas su de bzhin gsham //
NG0282:4928: rus pa brdung ba'i phye ma rnams //
NG0282:4929: thun gyi rdzas su bzhag kyang rung *//
NG0282:4930: rus byang thob pa'i kha la bzhag / ye shes lha yi skur bsgom la //
NG0282:4931: gnas rnams bsrung zhing snying po bzlas //
NG0282:4932: mdzes pa tsam du rab tu bzlas //
NG0282:4933: dregs pa can gyis las bya'i phyir //
NG0282:4934: pho mo sngags kyi bye brag las //
NG0282:4935: na yar bsgyur bas gang bsgrub 'grub //
NG0282:4936: mo la pho ru na yas bsgyur //
NG0282:4937: mo yi bdud mo pho las 'byung *//
NG0282:4938: pho yi bdud mo de bzhin no //
NG0282:4939: srog snying pho ru bsgyur ba 'di //
NG0282:4940: pho la bco lnga spyi sngags dang *//
NG0282:4941: thun rdzas rnams la mang du bzlas //
NG0282:4942: mchog gi phur pas yang dag gdab //
NG0282:4943: bstan pa bsrung ba'i las kyang bcol //
NG0282:4944: hu~m gdug pa 'dul ba dregs pa'i lha //
NG0282:4945: dregs pa rngam pa'i ral pa can //
NG0282:4946: mche ba gtsigs shing tshems brdar ba //
NG0282:4947: sku la zhing lpags rlon pa gsol //
NG0282:4948: ral pa bcings pa'i thor tshugs can //
NG0282:4949: g.yas pas dgra snying sbar gyis 'debs //
NG0282:4950: g.yon pa bdud kyi khram bam bsnams //
NG0282:4951: rngam pa'i tshems brdar spu gri'i so //
NG0282:4952: mche ba lcags kyi spu gri can //
NG0282:4953: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:4954: bstan pa gnyan por mi byed pa'i //
NG0282:4955: nyams pa gang yin snying la shad //
NG0282:4956: hu~m bdud kyi rgyal po ma rungs pa //
NG0282:4957: mun pa nag po'i kha dog la //
NG0282:4958: sku la dar nag ber mthing gsol //
NG0282:4959: ral pa nag po spyi bcings can //
NG0282:4960: lag na gcod pa'i s+t+wa re thogs //
NG0282:4961: dgra s+t+wa sdang ba'i dgra la thob //
NG0282:4962: mche ba dung gi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:4963: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:4964: dam nyams gang yin snying la ya //
NG0282:4965: hu~m 'jigs par byed pa'i bdud pho ni //
NG0282:4966: mon pa nag po rna cha can //
NG0282:4967: sku la stag lpags g.yang gzhi gsol //
NG0282:4968: ral pa nag po mun ltar @#//
NG0282:4970: lag na 'brel pa'i zor ba bsnams //
NG0282:4971: zor kha sdang ba'i dgra la ya //
NG0282:4972: mche ba lcags kyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:4973: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:4974: nyams pa gang yin snying la ya //
NG0282:4975: hu~m sgrol byed bdud kyi bshan pa ni //
NG0282:4976: mon pa nag po'i kha dog la //
NG0282:4977: sku la zhing gi g.yang gzhi la //
NG0282:4978: ral po nag po gyen la 'greng *//
NG0282:4979: lag na 'ching ba'i zhags pa thogs //
NG0282:4980: dam nyams gang yin 'ching bar byed / mche ba zangs kyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:4981: spu gri shad shad snying la bshad //
NG0282:4982: nyams pa gang yin snying la ya //
NG0282:4983: hu~m sha za khrag 'thung bdud kyi bu //
NG0282:4984: mon pa nag po me tri can //
NG0282:4985: sku la dred kyi pags pa la //
NG0282:4986: ral pa kham pa ya leb can //
NG0282:4987: lag na bsreg pa'i me dpung thogs //
NG0282:4988: nyams pa gang yin sreg par byed //
NG0282:4989: mche ba bse yi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:4990: spu gri shad shad snying la bshad //
NG0282:4991: nyams pa gang yin snying la ya //
NG0282:4992: dregs pa bdud kyi rgyal po la //
NG0282:4993: 'khor ni bdud nag stong gis bskor //
NG0282:4994: zhing lpags rlon pa'i stod thul can //
NG0282:4995: spyi bcings bdud kyi rigs rnams kyang *//
NG0282:4996: mche ba lcags kyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:4997: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:4998: bstan pa 'jig pa'i nyams pa la //
NG0282:4999: srog rtsa dmar po chod la shog khong khrag kha ru rngub par gyis //
NG0282:5000: chos shig rang gi dmag dpung chos //
NG0282:5001: phyor cig ru+u mtshon nag po phyor //
NG0282:5002: thob cig bdud kyi khram la thob //
NG0282:5004: zo zhig nyams pa'i sha la zo //
NG0282:5006: hu~m bdud kyi dmag dpung chi li li //
NG0282:5007: bdud kyi dmag sna da drongs shig / dam nyams dgra bo gang yin pa /
NG0282:5008: khram la thob cig bdud kyi tshogs //
NG0282:5009: hu~m ya bdud tshogs gyi gtso bo ni //
NG0282:5010: shel gyi mi pho dkar po la //
NG0282:5011: sku la bya rgod thul pa gsol //
NG0282:5013: nyi ma zla ba'i gdong pa can //
NG0282:5014: gser gyi so brdar khrigs se khrig / mche ba gser gyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:5015: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:5016: dam nyams kun gyi snying la shad //
NG0282:5017: chibs su dung gi rta pho chibs //
NG0282:5018: phum phum dmar po dar ltar 'phyar *//
NG0282:5019: dkar po kun gyi gtso bo ste //
NG0282:5020: dkar po 'bum la mnga' mdzad cing *//
NG0282:5021: 'od dkar lam gyi bdag po ste //
NG0282:5022: nyams pa 'di la rtags phyung zhig / hu~m shar phyogs srid pa'i rgyal po ni //
NG0282:5023: shel gyi 'od dkar lams se lam //
NG0282:5024: sku la bse khrab smug po gsol //
NG0282:5025: phyag na bse yi dung dmar bsnams //
NG0282:5026: mche ba dung gi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:5027: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:5028: smyo 'bog lhog rgod dus la bab //
NG0282:5029: hu~m lho phyogs srid pa'i rgyal po ste //
NG0282:5031: sku la lcags kyi tshem khrab gsol //
NG0282:5032: phyag na lcags kyi srin mo rkang *//
NG0282:5033: mche ba lcags kyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:5034: spu gri shad shad snying la bshad //
NG0282:5035: pho log nad kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5039: sku la zangs kyi tshem khrab gsol //
NG0282:5040: phyag na zangs kyi mdung dmar bsnams //
NG0282:5041: mche ba zangs kyi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:5042: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:5043: gzer nad nad kyi thun phob cig / hu~m byang phyogs srid pa'i rgyal po ste //
NG0282:5045: sku la bse yi tshem khrab gsol //
NG0282:5046: phyag na bse yi mdung dmar bsnams //
NG0282:5047: mche ba bse yi spu gri gtams //
NG0282:5048: spu gri shad shad snying la shad //
NG0282:5049: lhog rgal nad kyi thun phob cig / srid pa'i mnga' bdag kun la dbang //

NG0282:5051: srid pa'i rgyal po 'bum gyi bskor //

NG0282:5055: dmag dpung bsdu ba'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5056: srid pa'i rgyal pos dmag sna drongs //

NG0282:5062: shar phyogs btsan gyi dmag sna drongs //

NG0282:5064: srid pa btsan gyi rgyal po ste //
NG0282:5065: sngon po 'ja' dgu chibs su chibs //

NG0282:5067: phyag na zhags pa sngon po thogs //
NG0282:5068: gshin rje'i dmag dpung 'bum gyis bskor //
NG0282:5069: lho phyogs btsan gyi dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5070: gzer nad nad kyi thun phob cig / hu~m nub kyi srid pa'i yul rtse nas //
NG0282:5071: srid pa'i btsan gyi rgyal po ste //
NG0282:5072: dmar po zangs mdog chibs su chibs //
NG0282:5073: le brgan dmar po'i char chen gsol //
NG0282:5074: phyag na zhags pa dmar po thogs //
NG0282:5075: klu bdud dmag dpung 'bum gyis bskor //
NG0282:5076: nub phyogs btsan gyi dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5077: glang thabs nad kyi thun phob cig / hum byang phyogs srid pa'i yul rtse nas //
NG0282:5078: srid pa btsan gyi rgyal po de //
NG0282:5079: ljang gu spun dmar chibs su chibs //
NG0282:5080: na bza' ljang gu ber chen gsol //
NG0282:5081: phyag na zhags pa ljang gu thogs //
NG0282:5082: gnod sbyin dmag dpung 'bum gyis bskor //
NG0282:5083: byang phyogs btsan gyi dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5084: lhog rgal nad kyi thun phob cig / 'byung ba'i bdud bcom btsan chen yang *//
NG0282:5085: srog rtsa gcod cing sha la ya //
NG0282:5086: snying rtsa gcod cing snying khrag 'thung *//
NG0282:5087: bkrag dang mdangs la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NG0282:5088: nad kha dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5089: bstan pa bsrung ba'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5090: hum stong gsum rnam dag dmag gi sna 'dren pa //
NG0282:5091: dge bsnyen srung ma btsan gyi tshogs //
NG0282:5092: dus kyi 'khrug pa slong byed cing *//
NG0282:5093: mtshon gyi bskal pa 'bebs byed pa //
NG0282:5094: sku la za 'og ber chen gsol //
NG0282:5095: phyag na shel gyi rdo rje bsnams //
NG0282:5096: rol bas dbang bskur rang la dbang *//
NG0282:5099: rol du stong gsum 'khor gyis bskor //
NG0282:5100: rdo rje drag po dmag dpung 'joms //
NG0282:5101: gang du rbad par dmag sna 'dren //
NG0282:5102: bdud kyi dmag sna mun ltar 'dren //
NG0282:5103: btsan gyi dmag sna me ltar 'phro //
NG0282:5104: rgyal po'i dmag sna skar ltar 'khrug / ba dan ru mtshon me ltar 'bar //
NG0282:5105: ma bdud mang po mun ltar gtibs //
NG0282:5106: sha za mang po khra ltar lding */
NG0282:5107: khrag 'thung mang po mcho ltar rlob //
NG0282:5108: gang du rbad pa'i dmag sna 'dren //
NG0282:5109: shar gyi phyogs su dmag 'dren na //
NG0282:5110: ba dan dkar po rdzi la phyar //
NG0282:5111: lho yi phyogs su dmag 'dren na //
NG0282:5112: ba dan sngon po gnam ltar sngo //
NG0282:5113: nub kyi phyogs su dmag 'dren na //
NG0282:5114: ba dan dmar po me ltar 'bar //
NG0282:5115: byang gi phyogs su dmag 'dren na //
NG0282:5116: ba dan ljang gu chu ltar 'brub //
NG0282:5117: ru mtshon phyor zhing dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5118: gang du bsam pa'i chibs bskyod la //
NG0282:5119: bdud kyi mun pa char ltar phob //
NG0282:5120: btsan gyi sha bdal khrag tu skyugs //
NG0282:5121: rgyal po'i 'od zer skar ltar 'khrug / de yang dge bsnyen gnyan gyi grogs //
NG0282:5122: me ltar 'bar zhing dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5123: chu ltar 'brub cing dmag sna drongs //
NG0282:5124: b+h+yo b+h+yo gang yin las la thun phob cig / thun gyi las nyid drag por sbyar //
NG0282:5125: rgyu dus bzhi ru thun rnams brab //
NG0282:5126: ming byang gsal bar gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:5128: thod pa lud dang phur pa 'phar //
NG0282:5129: gtor ma me ru 'bar ba dang *//
NG0282:5130: bzhi po mngon du byung ba dang *//
NG0282:5131: drag sngags drag po'i thun gyis brab //
NG0282:5132: phur pa gdab cing mtshon gyis gtub //
NG0282:5133: thod pa 'phang zhing gtor ma gtang *//
NG0282:5135: nad rnams de bzhin shes par bya //
NG0282:5136: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:5137: drag po dregs pa bsgrub pa'i le'u ste nyi shu
NG0282:5138: bzhi pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das dregs
NG0282:5139: pa bsdus pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:5140: te // dregs pa bsdus te gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:5141: mtshan ngan rdzas kyi nang du yang *//
NG0282:5142: gtor ma ming byang bcug byas nas //
NG0282:5143: yi dam dam pa bsgom par bya //
NG0282:5144: gcig la mtha' bzhi spel ba'i sngags //
NG0282:5145: rang rang gang byed sngags su dbye //
NG0282:5146: yang na sngags kyi bye brag las //
NG0282:5147: dngos dang 'greng bu gi gu dang *//
NG0282:5148: na ro khyad par dbye bar bya //
NG0282:5149: rdzas kyi de bzhin rim par dbye //
NG0282:5150: thun yang de bzhin bstan par bya //
NG0282:5151: rang rang thun la rang rang sngags //
NG0282:5152: grangs dang rtags dang dus dag dang *//
NG0282:5153: gang yin las su rung bar bya //
NG0282:5154: bskul zhing rbad pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:5155: rang rang rdzas la brten par bya //
NG0282:5156: phyogs su 'phang pa'i las nyid bya //
NG0282:5158: gal te gnad du ma skyol na //
NG0282:5159: nag po spyi dkar thod pa ru //
NG0282:5160: de nyid snying dang khrag du bcas //
NG0282:5161: mon pa nag po'i snying yang rung *//
NG0282:5162: de yi nang du ming byang gzhug / re ba'i khug mar bcug kyang @#//
NG0282:5164: gsal ba'i lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NG0282:5165: gang yin dmigs pa gsal ba las //
NG0282:5166: dkar nag mtshams su drag sngags brdeg / de yi rtags la las sngags bya //
NG0282:5167: grangs su bstan pa'i las nyid de //
NG0282:5169: dkar po phrum dmar thod pa ru //
NG0282:5170: snying sna lnga la de bzhin bya //
NG0282:5171: ming dang rus yang bri bar bya //
NG0282:5172: thun rdzas sna tshogs mang du bltar //
NG0282:5173: gsal ba'i ting 'dzin dgongs pa yis //
NG0282:5174: rang bsrung gnad la dbab par bya //
NG0282:5175: thun rnams dus su brab par bya //
NG0282:5176: rtags nyid myur du byung ba dang *//
NG0282:5177: gang yin de la thod pa brdeg / de ni sa ru rtags byung na //
NG0282:5178: bsam pa'i 'bras bu chud mi za //
NG0282:5179: gang byas las la the tshom med //
NG0282:5180: mon pa nag po'i thod pa ru //
NG0282:5181: gang yin snying dang khrag blugs nas //
NG0282:5182: thun rnams rab tu brab byas te //
NG0282:5183: de nyid khol dang me ru+u 'bar //
NG0282:5185: de byung gang yin yul du brdeg / de yi bstan pa bsrung bar 'gyur //
NG0282:5186: sha ba dag gi thod pa ru //
NG0282:5187: gla ba lug dang bya rnams kyi //
NG0282:5188: snying dang khrag tu bcas pa blug / dam rdzas kun kyang tshang gyur na //
NG0282:5190: rim pa sngags kyi bya bar shes //
NG0282:5192: wa 'am spyang ki'i thod pa ru //
NG0282:5193: rim gyis shi ba'i khrag blugs la //
NG0282:5194: dug dang sbang mas brlan par bya //
NG0282:5195: zangs kyi dug rnams yang dag bstan //
NG0282:5196: sbyor ba sngags kyi na ya la //
NG0282:5197: gnad la dbab pa rab brdeg la //
NG0282:5198: nam gyi 'jing la thun yang brdeg / rtags rnams 'byung bar gdon mi za /
NG0282:5199: khams gsum gdug pa sgrol ba'i las //
NG0282:5200: gang du btab pa 'grub par byed //
NG0282:5201: bdud dang srin po gnod sbyin yang *//
NG0282:5203: yang dag min te gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:5205: las kyi srin po gdug pa'i mthus //
NG0282:5206: dam pa min te byin rlab 'byung *//
NG0282:5207: rtogs na yang dag nyid du 'gyur //
NG0282:5208: des na rtogs pa rab tu gces //
NG0282:5209: bden pa'i stobs la rab brten na //
NG0282:5210: nges bzung bral bas gang yang rung *//
NG0282:5212: 'ching med rab tu dgrol bar bya //
NG0282:5213: de ni sangs rgyas lag bcangs yin //
NG0282:5214: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NG0282:5215: bdud dang srin po thams cad btul //
NG0282:5216: rang rgyud ma yin rol par snang *//
NG0282:5217: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:5218: dregs pa bsdus te bsgrub pa'i le'u ste nyi shu lnga pa'o ///
NG0282:5219: / de nas bcom ldan 'das mkha' 'gro gdug byed
NG0282:5220: ma sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:5221: te / bstan pa gnyan po bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0282:5222: gdug byed srin mo rab tu sgrub //
NG0282:5223: de ni bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0282:5224: ya mtshan can du gyur pas na //
NG0282:5225: srid pa'i dbang chen rnam gsum yin //
NG0282:5226: dur khrod chen po gsar rnying can //
NG0282:5229: [(]14[)]@#// por spungs pa phung po can //
NG0282:5230: gdug pa'i sems can mang po gnas //
NG0282:5231: rngam pa'i sgra dang bcas pa'i gnas //
NG0282:5232: dur khrod srung dang dbang byed dang *//
NG0282:5233: sha za khrag 'thung mche ba dmar //
NG0282:5234: sha za mchu gug tshang yod dang *//
NG0282:5235: sa phyogs 'jigs pa'i gdug chen dang *//
NG0282:5236: de lta bu dang ldan pa ru //
NG0282:5237: mkha' 'gro gdug byed rab tu bsgrub //
NG0282:5238: man+dal mda' gang gru bzhi la //
NG0282:5239: rak+ta rnam gsum chag chag gdab //
NG0282:5240: dmar la 'od dang chas par bya //
NG0282:5241: dam rdzas lnga la de bzhin bya //
NG0282:5242: thig yang byin brlab rim pa ste //
NG0282:5243: hum las ye shes lnga bsams te //
NG0282:5244: de nyid rigs kyi lha lngar byung *//
NG0282:5245: spyan drang mchod pa byas nas su //
NG0282:5246: nam mkha' dag gi dkyil 'khor bsam //
NG0282:5247: sa la rim pa ma nor gdab //
NG0282:5248: tshon yang de bzhin rab tu brlab //
NG0282:5249: gru gsum zla gam mu khyud dang *//
NG0282:5251: snam bu sgo dang bcas pa la //
NG0282:5252: phyogs bzhir dur khrod chen po'i tshal //
NG0282:5253: mi ro mang po spungs pa bri //
NG0282:5254: mthing nag dmar dang dkar ba dang *//
NG0282:5255: gdan yang thod pa dmar por btang *//
NG0282:5256: 'khor lo phyogs dang mtshams su ser //
NG0282:5257: mi ro'i steng du mtshan ma bkod //
NG0282:5258: mu khyud nag cing thod pa dkar //
NG0282:5259: gru chad ljang zhing snam bu ser //
NG0282:5260: sgo ni rigs dang mthun pa dang *//
NG0282:5261: gzhi dmar thod pa dkar po btang //
NG0282:5262: gzhi ser lhu dum dkar por btang *//
NG0282:5263: gzhi ljang rgyu zhags dkar por btang *//
NG0282:5264: rin chen sna lnga'i brtsig pa la //
NG0282:5265: rin chen sna lnga'i phreng ba btang *//
NG0282:5266: lcags ri nag la me ri dmar //
NG0282:5267: de bzhin ma nor rim pa bri //
NG0282:5268: dbus su hum dang gdan du bcas //
NG0282:5269: phyogs bzhir rtsibs la ru bzhi dgod //
NG0282:5270: mtshams bzhi rtsibs la dza bzhi dgod //
NG0282:5271: sgo bzhir ya bzhir dgod par bya //
NG0282:5272: gcan gzan sha dang snying du bcas //
NG0282:5273: nag smug snying yang de bzhin te //
NG0282:5274: thod pa mtshan ldan bzhi ru bsham //
NG0282:5275: mi dbang 'bras bu sha khrag dang *//
NG0282:5276: mtshan ma tshol ba'i sha khrag dang *//
NG0282:5277: nag po'i snying dang sha khrag dang *//
NG0282:5278: mtshan ldan bzhi ru bsham par bya //
NG0282:5279: mtsho chen bzhi dang sha khrag dang *//
NG0282:5280: snying sna bzhi dang sha sna bzhi //
NG0282:5281: gru skyog bzhi ru yang dag bsham //
NG0282:5282: dbyings su sha khrag mang bstar nas //
NG0282:5283: dmar chen mtsho ltar bskyil ba bsham //
NG0282:5284: snying sna re dang rtsang rer bcas //
NG0282:5285: rang rang gdan steng dgod par bya //
NG0282:5286: ting 'dzin chen pos byin rlabs nas //
NG0282:5287: sngon du las rnams grub par bya //
NG0282:5288: dpal gyi gtor ma dbus su gzhag / phyi ma rang rang gnas su dgod //
NG0282:5289: yang na sder bu bzhi ru bya //
NG0282:5290: ling+ga dbul dang bstab pa dang *//
NG0282:5291: las rnams bstan pa'i gzhi yin pas //
NG0282:5292: rim pa ma nor grangs kyis bya //
NG0282:5293: dbus su dpal gyi sku bskyed nas //
NG0282:5294: yid 'bru rnams la ma mo bskyed //
NG0282:5295: spyan drang bstim dang mchod pa dang *//
NG0282:5296: phur pas gdab dang dbul bar bya //
NG0282:5297: bskul pa'i snying po'i las rnams @#//
NG0282:5299: bsnyen pa rkyang par dgra yis sdeb //
NG0282:5300: bag tsam zur tsam nor mi bya //
NG0282:5301: rkyang pa rim pa'i grangs gsum ste //
NG0282:5302: gsum dang gnyis dang gcig tu sdeb //
NG0282:5303: de yis gnad la dbab par 'gyur //
NG0282:5304: rang gi thun la ma lus bzlas //
NG0282:5305: thun phor bcu gnyis rang rang snod //
NG0282:5306: yang na bzhi dang gsum kyang rung *//
NG0282:5307: yang na thams cad 'dus pa'i thun //
NG0282:5308: bse phor kha sbyar nang du bya //
NG0282:5309: thun gsum sgor sgor byed kyang rung *//
NG0282:5310: bstod cing bskul te las rnams bcol //
NG0282:5312: bskang ba drag po de dus bya //
NG0282:5313: nyin dang mtshan du rab tu bskang *//
NG0282:5314: de bzhin las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:5315: sgrub pa drag po las la 'dzud //
NG0282:5316: snying po dril bas drag por 'gyur //
NG0282:5317: snying po bzhi las yang dag gcig / rbad pa nyid du de 'gro bas //
NG0282:5318: de yi dus su thun la brab //
NG0282:5319: gzugs la dus dus phur pa gdab //
NG0282:5320: thun yang khol dang mang bar 'byung *//
NG0282:5321: 'od dang du ba sgra snyan dang *//
NG0282:5322: spyugs pa glu dang me ru 'byung *//
NG0282:5323: sgra dang tshub ma kha ba dang *//
NG0282:5324: sems can dngos dang gzugs su 'byung *//
NG0282:5325: lung ston nges pa'i gdeng dang ldan //
NG0282:5326: rtags gnyis de ltar rab tu 'byung *//
NG0282:5327: de bzhin gtan la phebs pa dang *//
NG0282:5328: dbus kyi phur pa gdab bya zhing *//
NG0282:5329: mchog phur bcu gnyis gdab pa ste //
NG0282:5330: rang rang dus sngags bcas pas gdab //
NG0282:5331: thun yang de bzhin sngags kyis gdab //
NG0282:5332: lhag lhog bsregs te thun la blug / thun 'phang gtor ma bkra shis las //
NG0282:5333: yangs pa nyid du yang dag bstan //
NG0282:5334: dpal gyi pho nya'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5335: ya mtshan 'phrul gyi spyang mo ni //
NG0282:5336: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NG0282:5337: kha dgu gdangs shing shangs dgu snom //
NG0282:5338: spyan mig mtshal chu khol ma 'dra //
NG0282:5339: snyan ni srid pa gsum na nyan //
NG0282:5340: sgrol byed chibs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5341: phyogs bzhir rgyug cing cho nges 'debs //
NG0282:5342: zas su sems can 'bum za ma //
NG0282:5343: rgyug byed chibs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5344: nang yang sems can 'bum la za //
NG0282:5345: nub kyang sems can 'bum za ma //
NG0282:5346: rtag tu sha dang khrag la rngam //
NG0282:5347: za byed chibs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5348: le brgan dmar po'i ljags brkyangs pas //
NG0282:5349: nyams pa'i snying 'byin zangs kyi lce //
NG0282:5350: stong gsum dbang sgyur zangs kyi lce //
NG0282:5351: smra byed chibs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5352: bskyod pas rlung bas rab tu mgyogs //
NG0282:5353: mnos shing bsam pas yud kyis phyin //
NG0282:5354: stong gsum yud kyis sleb par mdzad //
NG0282:5355: bsams slebs chibs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5356: de 'dra'i lcags kyi spyang mo la //
NG0282:5357: lcags kyi mi mo bzang mo zhon //
NG0282:5358: shar gyi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5359: dri za'i dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5360: brgya byin 'khor bcas rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5361: sha rus za ba'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5362: lho yi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5363: gshin rje'i dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5364: me mo 'khor bcas rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5366: mdangs drod dang da khrol cig / nub kyi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5367: klu yi dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5368: ya bdud 'khor bcas rdul du rlogs /
NG0282:5370: byang gi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5371: gnod sbyin dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5372: nor srung 'khor bcas rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5373: dbugs 'phrog srog gcod dus la bab //
NG0282:5374: steng gi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5375: tshangs pa'i dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5376: nyi zla 'khor bcas rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5377: rnam shes dbral ba'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5378: 'og gi phyogs su rgyug pa'i tshe //
NG0282:5379: sa bdag dmag dpung dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5380: sa yi lha mo rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5381: sha rus dbral ba'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5382: sha la za zhing da tshur byon /
NG0282:5383: khrag la 'thung zhing da tshur byon //
NG0282:5384: rnam shes 'phrog la da tshur byon //
NG0282:5385: bdud kyi spyang mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5386: hum dpal gyi pho nya chen mo ni //
NG0282:5387: lcags kyi khyi mo rkang gsum ma //
NG0282:5388: stong gsum kun la dbang sgyur zhing *//
NG0282:5389: srid pa gsum la mnga' mdzad ma //
NG0282:5390: dbang byed chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5391: srin mo 'bum la mnga' mdzad ma //
NG0282:5392: gnod sbyin 'byung po thal bar rlogs //
NG0282:5393: bdud 'dul khyi mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5394: zas su sha gsum so brdar khrig / skom du khrag 'thung mchil za khrung *//
NG0282:5395: lha rkang za ba'i so brdar khrigs //
NG0282:5396: dug gsum rtsad gcod khyi mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5397: de 'dra'i lcags kyi khyi mo la //
NG0282:5398: lcags kyi mi mo bzang mo zhon //
NG0282:5399: 'jigs pa'i gzugs la khro gnyer can //
NG0282:5400: dpa' byed chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5401: phyogs bzhi'i rgyal po dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5402: rgyal phran mang po rdul du rlogs //
NG0282:5403: sum cu rtsa gsum mnga' mdzad ma //
NG0282:5404: dbang sdud chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5405: dbu la g.yag mgo thod du bcings //

NG0282:5424: rgyug byed wa mo'i dus la bab //

NG0282:5440: lag pa g.yas na phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:5441: rdo rje phur pa'i srung ma ste //

NG0282:5458: sha rus za ba'i dus la bab //

NG0282:5474: dbang sdud chen mo'i dus la bab //

NG0282:5478: sgrol byed chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5479: dur khrod sha la rngams pa'i tshe //

NG0282:5513: 'bigs byed mdung gi dus la bab //

NG0282:5517: thogs med mda' yi dus la bab //

NG0282:5551: bshan pa chen mo'i dus la bab //

NG0282:5556: chibs su dril rta rkang gsum chibs //

NG0282:5563: gdug byed rgyan pa'i dre'u rta'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5564: gong thag gong rmed sprul gyis brgyan //
NG0282:5565: khal du nad kyi rkyal pa bkal //
NG0282:5566: tshon gyi gru gu 'phong la bkal //
NG0282:5567: nad kyi bdag mo'i dus la @#//
NG0282:5569: mdun na shwa rde'u dkar nag 'grems //

NG0282:5756: ngan song 'joms par byed pa'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5757: spu rtse lcags su byung ba ni //
NG0282:5758: gdug pa can rnams 'joms byed cing *//
NG0282:5759: ci la'ang thogs med gdug pa sgrol //
NG0282:5760: gdug byed mtshon rtse'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5761: dpal ldan nag mo re ma dzu //
NG0282:5764: drag po sgrol byed dbang du sdud //
NG0282:5765: rak+sha gdug byed dus la bab //
NG0282:5766: zhal bgrad mche ba gtsigs pa yis //
NG0282:5767: khro mo 'bar ba'i cha lugs las //
NG0282:5768: gdug byed gang yin chems chems gsol /

NG0282:5771: srid pa gsum yang dbang du sdud //

NG0282:5774: gdug pa can gyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5775: ral pas stong khams bkang ba yis //
NG0282:5776: srid gsum dbang du sdud nas kyang *//
NG0282:5777: 'jig pa med pa drag por ston //
NG0282:5778: dbang sdud dbu skra'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5779: sku la me dpung 'bar ba yis //
NG0282:5780: stong khams thams cad sreg byed cing *//

NG0282:5783: phyag g.yas lcags kyi phur pa bsnams //
NG0282:5784: sgrol byed chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5785: dam nyams dgra bo sgrol bar byed //
NG0282:5786: srid pa'i gdar sha gcod pa'i rtags //
NG0282:5787: nyams pa sgrol byed dus la bab //
NG0282:5788: g.yon pa 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0282:5789: gang du 'bros par dbang med par //
NG0282:5790: gzung zhing rab tu 'chor mi srid //
NG0282:5791: 'dzin byed chen mo'i dus la bab //
NG0282:5792: zhabs kyis gdug pa'i klu rnams gnon //
NG0282:5793: gnon pa'i stabs kyi gar byed cing *//
NG0282:5795: gdug byed zhabs kyi dus la bab //
NG0282:5796: ngo mtshar chas kyis rab brgyan nas //
NG0282:5797: stong gsum sprul pa nag mos 'gengs //
NG0282:5798: gcig tu ma bab stong khams sgrol //
NG0282:5799: ngo mtshar lha yi dus la bab //
NG0282:5800: hum nag mo stong gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0282:5801: rab tu sprul cing bkye ba'i tshe //

NG0282:7596: po'i dbang thob shog / hum chos sku lhun grub thams cad thob //
NG0282:7597: 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyong mdzad pa //
NG0282:7598: bum pa rgyan ldan 'khor ba sol //
NG0282:7599: chos rnams lhun grub dbang thob shog / hum rigs lnga nyon mongs dug lnga 'joms //
NG0282:7600: ye shes lnga ru mnyam sbyar nas //
NG0282:7601: mtshon pas rang bzhin dbu la bzhugs //
NG0282:7602: ye shes lnga yi dbang thob shog / hum cod pan chos rnams mtshon pa ste //
NG0282:7603: snang srid chos kyi dar po che //
NG0282:7604: bde gshegs kun kyang mnyam sbyar bas //
NG0282:7605: cod pan dam pa'i dbang thob shog / hum rigs lnga rgyal bas don mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7606: rigs lnga mtshon phyed dam pa dang *//
NG0282:7607: gang 'dul bsan pa rgyas mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7608: rigs kyi mtshan ma'i dbang thob shog / hum yi ge 'bru lnga ye shes lnga //
NG0282:7609: mtshon byed don gyi snying po ste //
NG0282:7610: snying po dam pa lha yi sku //
NG0282:7611: 'bru lnga snying po'i dbang thob shog / hum gdug pa 'joms shing ye shes gsal //
NG0282:7612: sku lnga mtshon byed phyag mtshan lnga //
NG0282:7613: rgyal ba 'byung ba'i rang rtags te //
NG0282:7614: phyag mtshan lnga yi dbang thob shog / hum dug lnga'i mtshon gyis mi tshugs pa'i //
NG0282:7615: gser gyi rdo rje rab tu mtshon //
NG0282:7616: dpa' rtul stag gi rgyan cha can //
NG0282:7617: 'joms byed go cha'i dbang thob shog / hum dus gsum 'phags pa mchod mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7618: rin chen mdzes su sdug pa yis //
NG0282:7619: dang ba'i stobs kyis mchod pa yi //
NG0282:7620: me tog dam pa'i dbang thob shog / hum dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku yi rgyan //
NG0282:7621: 'khor rnams rab tu mnyes mdzad pa //
NG0282:7622: nyes pas ma gos dbu la bskor //
NG0282:7623: rgyal mtshan gdugs kyi dbang thob shog / ro mchog lnga ldan zhal zas la //
NG0282:7624: dbul zhing phongs pa sel mdzad pa //
NG0282:7626: zhal zas mod la dbang thob shog / hum kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NG0282:7627: thugs rjes khams gsum gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:7628: gnyen po las su rung mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7629: 'jigs byed gnyen po'i dbang thob shog / hum gsung gi rang bzhin mtshon byed pa'i //
NG0282:7630: le brgan 'bar ba'i kha dog la //
NG0282:7631: snying po nus pa'i don dang ldan //
NG0282:7632: nus pa can gyi dbang thob shog / hum tsit+ta smug po'i gzhal yas na //
NG0282:7633: khams gsum dbang gi bdag po ste //
NG0282:7634: brkyang bskum rab tu gdengs pa yis //
NG0282:7635: gdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog / hum thugs ka rin chen zur brgyad las //
NG0282:7636: phrin las sna tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NG0282:7637: thams cad kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NG0282:7638: ye shes sems dpa'i dbang thob shog / hum steng gi phyogs la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7639: gdug pa tshangs pa ma lus 'dul //
NG0282:7640: ye shes chen po'i byin rlabs yin //
NG0282:7641: gdug pa 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog / hum steng gi yum chen za byed ma //
NG0282:7642: tshangs pa mo yi gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:7643: rang byung ye shes byin rlabs yin //
NG0282:7644: steng gi yum chen dbang thob shog / hum gdug pa tshangs pa'i 'khor 'joms pa //
NG0282:7647: za byed chen mo mche ba can //
NG0282:7648: phag gi mgo can dbang thob shog / hum tshangs pa chen po'i 'khor 'joms pa //
NG0282:7649: gdug byed chen mo rab tu 'joms //
NG0282:7650: gdug pa rtsad gcod bsam sleb ma //
NG0282:7651: gshog pa can gyi dbang thob shog / hum rang byung rgyal po dam rdzas lnga //
NG0282:7652: bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin te //
NG0282:7653: rtogs na rang byung sangs rgyas lnga //
NG0282:7654: bdud rtsi lnga yi dbang thob shog / hum khyad par dpal gyi gtor ma 'di //
NG0282:7656: snang srid gtor ma'i rang bzhin te //
NG0282:7657: khyad par gtor ma'i dbang thob shog / hum rang byung rgyal po lha yi rgyan //
NG0282:7658: mdzes pas rab tu brgyan pa ste //
NG0282:7659: lha la rab tu mdzes pas brgyan //
NG0282:7660: dbu rgyan cod pan dbang thob shog / hum rnam thar dgu dang rab ldan pa'i //
NG0282:7661: theg pa dgu yi sgo gnas nas //
NG0282:7662: khyad par chen po ngan song 'joms //
NG0282:7663: sa dgu gnon pa'i dbang thob shog / hum ye shes lnga dang rab ldan pa'i //
NG0282:7664: rdo rje rtse lnga ye shes lnga //
NG0282:7666: dug lnga 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog / hum ye shes me dpung 'bar ba ste //
NG0282:7667: thugs mchog rab tu 'bar ba'i rtags //
NG0282:7668: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad sreg / nyon mongs
NG0282:7669: sreg pa'i dbang thob shog / hum mtshon gyi rgyal
NG0282:7671: sku gsum lhun grub rtse mos mtshan //
NG0282:7672: ngan song gsum po rtag tu sgrol //
NG0282:7673: dug gsum rtsad gcod dbang thob shog / hum thugs rje'i phur pas gdug pa 'dul //
NG0282:7674: bgegs kyi rgyal po sgrol mdzad pa //
NG0282:7675: 'khor ba bdar gcod dbyings su sgrol //
NG0282:7676: gdug pa 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog / hum zhag gi zo ris dam rdzas bcud kyi rgyan //
NG0282:7677: thal chen tshom bu 'khor ba 'joms pa'i rtags //
NG0282:7678: rak+ta'i thig le thugs rje chags pa'i rtags //
NG0282:7679: mtshan ma rnam pa gsum gyi dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7680: hum thod pa rlon pa chos kyi sku yi rtags
NG0282:7681: // thod pa skam po longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rtags //
NG0282:7682: thod pa tshal bu sprul pa sku yi rtags //
NG0282:7683: sku gsum mtshon byed thod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7684: hum rigs bzhi klu rnams ma lus 'dul ba'i rtags
NG0282:7685: // gdug pa sbrul ni rigs bzhis sku la brgyan //
NG0282:7686: zhe sdang chen po gnas su 'joms mdzad pa //
NG0282:7687: gdug pa chas kyi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7688: hum ye shes me dpung 'khor ba sreg pa'i rtags
NG0282:7689: // ye shes me ri ljang ser dmar po'i 'od //
NG0282:7690: mdor na ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin te //
NG0282:7691: dug lnga sreg pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7692: hum kham nag ral pa kun gyi rgyan du bcings
NG0282:7693: // srid pa'i rtse mo zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NG0282:7694: gti mug chen po rtsad nas bcad nas kyang *//
NG0282:7695: dbu skra ral pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7696: hum tshon gang sku yi ba spu'i bu ga rnams
NG0282:7697: // thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs cir yang snang *//
NG0282:7698: rdo rje phur pa rab tu ki la ya //
NG0282:7700: dbang thob shog / hum ye shes rdo rje rab tu 'bar ba yis //
NG0282:7701: rdo rje gshog pas khams gsum zil gyis gnon //
NG0282:7702: gdug byed rang dbyung med par gnon mdzad par //
NG0282:7703: rdo rje gshog pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7704: hum zhing chen g.yang gzhis 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod
NG0282:7705: // glang chen ko rlon thugs rje stobs kyi bdag
NG0282:7706: / stag sham phrin las thams cad rgyas pa'i rtags
NG0282:7707: // // bdud chas dpa' bo'i dbang rnams thob par
NG0282:7708: shog / hum rdo rje thod khrag rab tu gsol
NG0282:7709: // // ba yis / khams gsum chags pa rab tu zhi bar mdzad //
NG0282:7710: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod byed thod pa'i khrag /
NG0282:7711: rak+ta chen po'i dbang mchog thob par shog / hum
NG0282:7712: cod pan dmar sngo rab tu 'phur byed pa'i //
NG0282:7713: thabs dang shes rab sna gnyis tshon du ldan //
NG0282:7714: 'khor ba dbyings su 'dren pa'i mtshan ma ste //
NG0282:7715: rab tu brgyan pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7716: hum dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus mnyes mdzad pa
NG0282:7717: / khams gsum 'khor ba'i bag chags spyod mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:7718: lha mo lnga dang ldan pa'i mchod pa yis //
NG0282:7719: mchod pa rgya cher mchod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7720: hum dngos med sku la rgyal bar bzhengs mdzad pa'i
NG0282:7721: // bzlas brjod grangs kyi snying po rab tu 'bul //
NG0282:7722: thugs dam chen po bsnyen pa 'bul ba'i rten //
NG0282:7723: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7724: hum 'jig rten khams rnams dbang du sdud pa yi
NG0282:7725: // lcags kyi spyang mo khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0282:7726: mngags pas pho nya'i tshul te rngam pa'i gdangs //
NG0282:7727: dbang sdud dam can dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7728: khyi mo ral bas khams gsum dngangs pa'i bdag /
NG0282:7729: khams gsum zas su za ba'i rkan sgra can //
NG0282:7730: srid gsum skom du 'thung ba'i hub sgra can //
NG0282:7731: dam can mkha' 'gro'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7732: hum 'phar ba lce brgyad snang srid sil bur 'don
NG0282:7733: // khams gsum kun tu phyogs bzhi'i dmag dpung 'joms //
NG0282:7734: nga ro chen po phyogs bcu kun tu sgrogs //
NG0282:7735: mkha' 'gro rgyas pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7736: hum zangs kyi wa mos snang srid gdug pa 'dul
NG0282:7737: // ri rab rtse nas snyil ba'i dbang mo che //
NG0282:7738: tsit+ta don snying za ba'i rkan sgra can //
NG0282:7739: dbang sdud mkha' 'gro'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7740: hum khams gsum nad kyi bdag mo dbang sgyur ma
NG0282:7741: // 'jig rten khams kun khyab pa'i bya ma rta //
NG0282:7742: mi phyugs kun la mnga' mdzad dbang mo che //
NG0282:7743: gdug pa ma mo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7744: hum dus gsum kun tu rgyal ba'i sku brnyes pa
NG0282:7745: // bstan pa rgyas pa'i slad du phrin las mdzad //
NG0282:7746: ser nag chen mo khams gsum kun gyi bdag /
NG0282:7747: mkha' 'gro dbang sdud dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7748: hum las su sha khrag ro la rngam pa'i yum
NG0282:7749: / khrag 'thung dmar nag srid gsum dbang du sdud //
NG0282:7750: stong khams dge sdig bya ra byed pa'i @#//
NG0282:7752: dad pa stobs ldan mkha' 'gro'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7753: hum phrin las sna tshogs mthar phyin grub pa mo
NG0282:7754: // rgya mtsho'i gting gi klu rnams 'khrug byed ma //
NG0282:7755: ljang nag chen mo'i phrin las mthar phyin ma //
NG0282:7756: mkha' 'gro mthu yi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7757: hum bdud kyi rigs rnams dbang du sdud mdzad ma
NG0282:7758: // mthing nag bdud kyi chas su rab tu zhugs /
NG0282:7759: khams gsum bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dbang mo che //
NG0282:7760: gdug pa bdud 'dul dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7761: hum 'jig rten gnod byed rab tu 'dul mdzad ma
NG0282:7762: // ser bas rgyas pa'i rang bzhin mtshon mdzad ma //
NG0282:7763: ki kang las kyis bskal par 'dul mdzad ma //
NG0282:7764: mkha' 'gro mthu byin dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7765: hum khams gsum gang 'dul dbang gi bdag mo ste
NG0282:7766: // rak+sha srin po za byed dbang du sdud //
NG0282:7767: dpal gyi bka' nyan khrag gi dri snom ma //
NG0282:7768: dbang phyug chen mo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7769: hum gdug pa klu rnams rab tu 'dul mdzad ma
NG0282:7770: // nad ngan phrin las dbang gi bdag mo ste //
NG0282:7771: klu la mnga' mdzad nad kyi bdag mo yang *//
NG0282:7772: las rnams mthar phyin dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7773: hum 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba'i las mdzad ma
NG0282:7774: // grangs dang ldan pa ma nor rim par ldan //
NG0282:7775: rnam bzhi rtogs pa'i khyad par ston mdzad pa //
NG0282:7776: yang dag don dang ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7777: hum thugs mchog rang byung ye shes 'od dang ldan
NG0282:7778: // 'khor ba'i mun pa ma lus sel mdzad pa //
NG0282:7779: rgyal ba'i thugs la nyon mongs nyes pa med //
NG0282:7780: snang ba mar me'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7781: hum gdug pa chen po thabs kyis 'dul mdzad pa
NG0282:7782: // mthing nag drag pos thams cad 'joms pa'i sku //
NG0282:7783: zhal gsum phyag drug zur gsum dbal dang ldan //
NG0282:7784: sgrub pa drag po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7785: hum nyung dkar rgyal pos thams cad sgrol ba'i dbang
NG0282:7786: *// khro bo'i rgyal po 'bum phrag bsam las 'das //
NG0282:7787: stong gsum khro bos dus gcig khengs mdzad pa //
NG0282:7788: nyung dkar rgyal po sgrol ba'i dbang rnams thob par
NG0282:7789: shog / hum gu gul sbyar ba'i rdzas kyi dam
NG0282:7790: pa ste // ye shes lnga brnyes nyes byed rten dang 'bral //
NG0282:7791: rab tu bsgrubs pas 'od dang du bar ldan //
NG0282:7792: drag po rdzas kyi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7793: hum dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas lhun gyis grub
NG0282:7794: // rang bzhin ye shes lha rnams bzhugs pa'i rten //
NG0282:7795: mthing nag gru gsum pho brang dbus gsal ba'i //
NG0282:7796: pho brang chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7797: hum 'khor ba nyon mongs ma lus sreg pa ste
NG0282:7798: // me yi rgyal po drang srong rab tu 'bar //
NG0282:7799: thams cad sreg par byed pa me yi dbang *//
NG0282:7800: nyon mongs rang rgyud sreg pa'i dbang rnams thob par
NG0282:7801: shog / hum thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel
NG0282:7802: pa'i rtags // drag po hom la rab tu mchod par @#//
NG0282:7804: sreg byed drang srong mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0282:7805: mchod 'bul dgang blug dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7806: hum zhe sdang chen po rab tu gnon mdzad pa
NG0282:7807: // rdo rje rgya gram phrin las mthar phyin pa //
NG0282:7808: gang la bya ba'i las nyid gdon mi za //
NG0282:7809: gnon byed rgya gram dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7810: hum gzas pa bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa la
NG0282:7811: // rten dang phral ba'i phra mar rab tu bsngags //
NG0282:7812: rang gi rdzas la dbye ba'i dbang dang ldan //
NG0282:7813: zhing bcu dbye ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7814: hum phye nas rab tu bsgral ba'i don mdzad pa
NG0282:7815: // nga rgyal rang khar 'dzin pa sgrol mdzad pa //
NG0282:7816: zhe sdang rang rgyud ngan song gnas su ltung *//
NG0282:7817: stong pa chen por sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7818: hum gti mug sha yi mchod pa ri rab tsam
NG0282:7819: // 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho kyi li li //
NG0282:7820: zhe sdang rus pa'i mchod pa khra la la //
NG0282:7821: dug gsum zhal du gsol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7822: hum khams gsum dbang du sdud mdzad sgrol byed sku
NG0282:7823: // nyon mongs thang gcig yud la sgrol mdzad pa //
NG0282:7824: rdo rje phur pa zhing bcu sgrol ba'i lha /
NG0282:7825: khams gsum dbyings su sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog / rdo rje phur pa rab tu ki la ya //
NG0282:7826: zhing bcu sgrol mdzad badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7827: ru tra gnas su sgrol mdzad badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7828: nyon mongs dbyings su sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7829: hum 'khor ba rang rgyud ngan song dbyings su 'khyams
NG0282:7830: // 'dzin pa sgrol phyir mtshon gyi rgyal po dang *//
NG0282:7831: mkha' 'gro gdug byed phyag chas dbyings su sgrol //
NG0282:7832: 'joms byed mtshon gyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NG0282:7833: hum drag po mtshon gyi rgyal po gtor ma la
NG0282:7834: // ngar 'dzin rab tu brtas pas gcod par byed //
NG0282:7835: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i zangs dang lcags //
NG0282:7836: gcod byed ral gri'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7837: hum nyon mongs dug lnga drug gis 'thibs par byed
NG0282:7838: // rul cing myags pas 'khor ba gting nas skems //
NG0282:7839: gnyen po'i dbang du thabs las de ltar snang *//
NG0282:7840: nyon mongs zhen pa sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7841: hum khyad par chen po 'bar bas zhen pa gcod
NG0282:7842: // sna lngas mtshon las nad lngas 'khor ba nyen //
NG0282:7843: de nyid rgyal bas byin rlabs rab tu gsungs //
NG0282:7844: zhen pa gcod pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7845: hum gtun khung gru gsum yum gyi mkha' dbyings su
NG0282:7846: // rig pa ye shes yab kyi rdo rje 'di //
NG0282:7847: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i rtags //
NG0282:7848: rdo rje tho ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7849: hum khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir
NG0282:7850: // 'brel pa'i lha mchog badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7851: gang yin stong byed mthu 'phrog badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7852: gdug byed stobs dang bral ba'i dbang thob shog /
NG0282:7853: hum khams gsum nyon mongs gnas su drang ba'i phyir
NG0282:7854: // rab tu 'gugs byed badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7855: nyon mongs zhing bcu gnas su 'dren mdzad pa //
NG0282:7857: gdug pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog / hum nyon mongs rang gar mi gtang bcing ba'i phyir //
NG0282:7858: rab tu 'ching byed badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7859: zhing bcu 'ching byed badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7860: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7861: hum gdug pa can rnams rab tu 'dul ba'i phyir
NG0282:7862: // smyo byed chen po badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7863: nyon mongs 'joms phyir badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7864: smyo byed chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7865: hum gdug pa thabs kyis sgrol ba 'jigs pa'i sku
NG0282:7866: // nyon mongs sgrol byed badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7867: zhen pa'i dngos po rab tu gcod byed pa'i //
NG0282:7868: sgrol ba chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NG0282:7869: hum gdos pa'i dngos po brlag par bya ba'i phyir
NG0282:7870: // stob byed chen mo badzra ki la ya //
NG0282:7871: gdangs pa'i zhal du nyon mongs stob byed pa //
NG0282:7872: stob byed chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog / dngos grub dam pa lha yi lha //
NG0282:7873: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NG0282:7874: dur khrod rdzas la brten te bsgrubs lags na //
NG0282:7875: snang srid byams pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:7876: ye shes lha ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NG0282:7877: dngos grub stsal dang stsol bar mi dmigs kyang *//
NG0282:7878: gdug pa chen po thabs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0282:7879: drag pos 'dren pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:7880: hum chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:7881: dregs pa 'dul ba'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs 'byung *//
NG0282:7882: bdud kyi rgyal pos ru tra 'dul ba ltar //
NG0282:7883: bdud rgyal dregs pa 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0282:7884: hum bdud dpung choms nas chos nyid don mthong bas //
NG0282:7885: bdud rgyal ru tras chos nyid don rtogs nas //
NG0282:7886: thugs rje'i byin rlabs bdud la snang ba ltar //
NG0282:7887: nyon mongs dbyings su bsgral ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NG0282:7888: hum 'khor gyis gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0282:7889: steng phyogs khro rgyal yab yum 'khor dang bcas //
NG0282:7890: tshangs pa 'khor bcas rab tu btul ba ltar //
NG0282:7891: 'jig rten dregs pa btul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
