NG0282:8223: gang yin nyams pa 'phung bar byed //
NG0282:8224: dmag sna drong shig drag po zor gyi lha //
NG0282:8226: drag po zor gyi thun phob cig / rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:8227: drag po zor gyi le'u ste so drug pa'o //
NG0282:8228: // de nas bcom ldan 'das rab tu dbye ba
NG0282:8229: dang bsgral ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:8230: te / dbye ba'i sa phyogs gang yin par //
NG0282:8231: rim pa gsum gyi gru gsum la //
NG0282:8232: dpangs su khru gang pa gcig brtsig / gu gul
NG0282:8233: chu yis legs par byug / rnam gnyis las su
NG0282:8234: bstan pa'i phyir // lho ru sgo re yang dag bsham //
NG0282:8235: dme ba'i rdzas lnga de bzhin bya //
NG0282:8236: tshon skud gnyis kyis rtsa ba bsdam //
NG0282:8237: zhing gi rgyus pa'i thag pas gdags //
NG0282:8238: yi ge gnyis kyi bar dag tu //
NG0282:8239: dbye ba'i lha nyid gzhug par bya //
NG0282:8240: dbye ba'i snying po rgyab tu bri //
NG0282:8241: rnam gsum rdzas kyis mchod pa'i phyir //
NG0282:8242: de nyid gsum yang rab tu gdams //
NG0282:8243: ting 'dzin rim pas bsgom bya ste //
NG0282:8244: dpal du bskyed dang las mkhan bsgom //
NG0282:8245: spyan drang bstim dang mchod pa dang *//
NG0282:8246: dbye ba'i sngags nyid mang du bzlas //
NG0282:8247: bstod cing bskul te mchod pa 'bul //
NG0282:8248: dbye ba'i rtags nyid byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8249: thun rnams brab cing rab tu rbad //
NG0282:8250: sgro gnyis las kyi rlung la phyar //
NG0282:8251: las kyi lung gis khyer bar 'gyur //
NG0282:8252: hum nye 'byed las kyi phra ma mkhan //
NG0282:8253: rlung lha'i bu la srin po'i tsha //
NG0282:8254: pha ni rlung lha kha skyes ram pa yin //
NG0282:8255: ma ni srin mo kha 'bar ma //
NG0282:8256: gnyis med bu gcig byung ba ni //
NG0282:8257: nye 'byed chen mo phra ma mkhan //
NG0282:8258: sku mdog dud kha chen mo la //
NG0282:8259: 'jigs pa'i khro gnyer mang pos brgyan //
NG0282:8260: g.yas kyi dang po bya rog gong ru bsnams //
NG0282:8261: nyams pa spyan gyis gzigs par byed //
NG0282:8262: g.yon gyi dang po 'ug pa'i gong du bsnams //
NG0282:8263: mi 'chor rtog pa rab tu gsal //
NG0282:8264: g.yas 'og lcags kyu s+t+wa re bsnams //
NG0282:8265: nyams pa mgo lus 'bral ba'i rtags //
NG0282:8266: g.yon gyi 'og ma rlung gi rkyal pa bsnams //
NG0282:8267: nyams pa rlung la skur ba'i rtags //
NG0282:8268: khyod kyi phrag pa g.yas pa na //
NG0282:8269: lcags kyi bya khra g.yu mig can //
NG0282:8270: snang srid mi mthong gcig kyang med //
NG0282:8271: dam nyams phrag pa g.yas kyi pho lha phrol /
NG0282:8272: khyod kyi phrag pa g.yon pa na //
NG0282:8273: zangs kyi bya khra gser mig can //
NG0282:8274: srid pa gsum yang dus gcig gzigs //
NG0282:8275: phrag pa g.yon gyi mo lha phrol /
NG0282:8276: khyod kyi spyi bo'i gtsug rum na //
NG0282:8277: shel gyi bya khyung g.yu mig can //
NG0282:8278: dge sdig gnyis kyi las kyang gzigs //
NG0282:8279: 'go bar byed pa'i lha dang phrol /
NG0282:8280: khyod kyi rgyab kyi sog pa la //
NG0282:8281: stag dang spyang ki rngam zhing rgyug / nyams pa zas su za bar byed //
NG0282:8285: khyod kyi mdun gyi lhe sna la //
NG0282:8287: snang srid dbang du sdud par byed //
NG0282:8288: dam nyams mdun gyi srog lha phrol /
NG0282:8289: khyod ni stong gsum phra ma mkhan //
NG0282:8290: rlung lha'i bu la srin bu'i tsha //
NG0282:8291: mchu ni lcags kyi gzong bas rno //
NG0282:8292: dam nyams mi dang lha yi bar du dbyen chug cig / khyod kyis mi byed gang yang med //
NG0282:8293: lha dang lha min g.yul 'gyed kyang *//
NG0282:8294: 'byed par khyod kyis nus par byed //
NG0282:8295: tshe gsum dran byed pho rog ma //
NG0282:8296: khyod kyis mi dran ci yang med //
NG0282:8297: bstan pa gnyen la gnod pa yi //
NG0282:8298: dam nyams bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'di //
NG0282:8299: 'go bar byed pa'i lha dang phrol //
NG0282:8300: stongs par byed pa'i gnyen dang phrol //
NG0282:8301: hu lu mun mthong 'ug pa mo //
NG0282:8302: khyod kyis mi mthong gang yang med //
NG0282:8303: bstan pa gnyen la gnod byed pa'i //
NG0282:8304: dam nyams bsgral ba'i zhing bcu 'di //
NG0282:8305: khyod kyis bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NG0282:8306: ces so so'i sgro gnyis las kyi rlung la phyar ro //
NG0282:8307: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:8308: zhing bcu lha dang dbye ba'i le'u ste so bdun
NG0282:8309: pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das gnod sbyin
NG0282:8310: sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te
NG0282:8311: / dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:8312: dkyil 'khor gru gsum byas nas su //
NG0282:8313: steng du sol me rab tu btang *//
NG0282:8314: thal chen sol bas nang byugs la //
NG0282:8315: zhabs ma dmar po'i gdan bting la //
NG0282:8316: ling+ga bya ba'i rgyud nyid la //
NG0282:8317: ling+ga rab tu bzos byas la //
NG0282:8318: ske nas sngo dmar rab tu gdags //
NG0282:8319: drag po rtsang la bstod par bya //
NG0282:8320: nag po skra yis skye gnas btags //
NG0282:8321: phur pa nyid la bstod par bya //
NG0282:8322: rtsa gnyis kyi ni khrag gis byugs //
NG0282:8323: thod pa mtshan dang ldan pa ru //
NG0282:8324: dmar po gnyis kyi snying khrag la //
NG0282:8325: de bzhin bsre ba'i rdzas rnams dang *//
NG0282:8326: de bzhin zur la rab tu gzhag / bse phor mtshan ldan nang dag tu //
NG0282:8327: chang dang rin chen sna lnga dang *//
NG0282:8328: 'bru la sogs te zur du gzhag / tsa ra khrag gis byugs pa yi //
NG0282:8329: phur pa'i rtse mo gnam du bstan //
NG0282:8330: rab tu zur la dgod par bya //
NG0282:8331: de la sogs pa'i rdzas rnams ni //
NG0282:8332: snying sna khrag sna mang du \u0f84bsags //
NG0282:8333: lha nyid gsal la gnas rnams bsrung *//
NG0282:8334: de nyid las su rung ba dang *//
NG0282:8335: dregs pa can gyi sngags la 'jug / gong du bstan pa de bzhin du //
NG0282:8336: nur ba med pa rab tu bzlas //
NG0282:8337: ci bgyi bka' nyan bran ltar khol //
NG0282:8338: the tshom som nyi ma yin par //
NG0282:8339: dregs pa'i srog snying mang du bzlas //
NG0282:8340: hum bstan pa gnyen po bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NG0282:8341: rdo rje phur pa'i srung ma dam tshig can //
NG0282:8342: khas blangs dam bcas srog gi snying po phul //
NG0282:8343: bstan pa rgyas pa'i slad du don mdzad pa'i //
NG0282:8344: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0282:8345: dregs pa'i mnga' mdzad gnod sbyin me ru tse /
NG0282:8346: khrag mdog dmar po bse yi ral pa can //
NG0282:8349: smin ma glog 'gyu bar snang go skabs 'byed //
NG0282:8350: shangs nas bu yug rdo rje thog chen 'bebs //
NG0282:8351: zhal bgrad tshems ni spu gri 'bum gyis gtams //
NG0282:8352: rngam pa'i ljags 'dril bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NG0282:8353: ag tshom dmar ser dug gsum rtsad nas bsreg / snyan nas 'brug stong sgra skad ldi ri ri //
NG0282:8354: sen mo lcags kyu'i rtse ltar 'dzin zhing 'gugs //
NG0282:8355: ba spu'i nang nas gnam lcags zhun chu 'brub //
NG0282:8356: spyan mig dmar pos snang srid gsal bar mdzad //
NG0282:8357: lcags kyus snang srid dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NG0282:8358: smin ma 'dzings pas me stag rab tu 'phro //
NG0282:8359: yak+sha gnod sbyin 'jigs pas rab tu rngam //
NG0282:8360: chu ltar 'brub cing me ltar sreg par byed //
NG0282:8361: zhabs kyis gang du bsams par yud kyis phyin //
NG0282:8362: na bza' dmar po sprin gyi g.yang gzhi gsol //
NG0282:8363: nyams pa'i snying 'byin chad par bcug nas gsol //
NG0282:8364: rdo rje phur pa'i las rnams khyed kyis sgrubs //
NG0282:8365: bcol pa'i las rnams ma lus 'grub par mdzod //
NG0282:8366: hum gnod sbyin me ru tse yi thugs dam dgyes skul ma //
NG0282:8367: yum gcig rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0282:8368: khros pa'i sku mdog khrag gi thigs pa 'dra //
NG0282:8369: mi bzad rdo rje lcags kyi phur pas gtams //
NG0282:8370: rdo rje'i ral pa si li li /
NG0282:8371: khrag gi mchi ma phru lu lu //
NG0282:8372: snying rje mi mnga' dam nyams sgrol bar byed //
NG0282:8373: phyag na rdo rje phur pa 'dril zhing 'debs //
NG0282:8374: dus la bab bo gar kyi dbang phyug ma //
NG0282:8375: gru bzhi srin mo sbrul 'dra ma //
NG0282:8376: yab yum rtags dang gdug pa can //
NG0282:8377: bya ba ma yin rab tu gzem //
NG0282:8378: rta dang byis pa mug pa'am //
NG0282:8379: tsag tsog mang po byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8380: khug pas rab tu gdab bya ste //
NG0282:8381: phur pa blangs shing rab tu 'dril //
NG0282:8382: drod dang tshangs pa'i mgo la gdab //
NG0282:8383: sa ti yam shud rkang pa la //
NG0282:8384: shu la khu le lag pa la //
NG0282:8385: da sha gri ba gsang ba la //
NG0282:8386: rtsa gnyis yab yum sngags kyis gdab //
NG0282:8387: yab snying yum lte rnam pa gnyis //
NG0282:8388: rab tu gdab pa de bzhin bya //
NG0282:8389: gyad kyi sku mdog bzhir bsgom la //
NG0282:8390: phur pa gdab cing las rnams bya //
NG0282:8391: gtor ma lag tu thogs byas la //
NG0282:8392: srod la zla ba'i 'od la bskul //
NG0282:8393: tho rangs skar chen shar nas bskul //
NG0282:8394: dgong mo grib so chags la bskul //
NG0282:8395: nang par nyi ma'i rtse la bskul //
NG0282:8396: rang bzhin rtags ni byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8397: gang yin phyogs su gtor ma 'phangs //
NG0282:8399: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:8400: gnod sbyin dregs pa can sgrub pa'i le'u ste so
NG0282:8401: brgyad pa'o // // de nas bcom ldan 'das yon
NG0282:8402: tan bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NG0282:8403: te / bstan pa thams cad 'phel ba dang *//
NG0282:8404: chos nyid zhi bas 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:8405: ma rig rig par 'gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:8406: ston pa rang las byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8409: rgyud gnyis yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8410: zhi ba chen por rtogs pa dang *//
NG0282:8411: ma rig mun pa bsal ba dang *//
NG0282:8412: rig pa'i ye shes gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:8413: rtogs pas 'bras bur gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:8414: dri med 'od ldan gsal ba dag / rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8415: kun bzang don nyid ston pa dang *//
NG0282:8416: de nyid gzhi ru gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:8417: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa dang *//
NG0282:8418: de yis thams cad chos ston dang *//
NG0282:8419: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8420: chos nyid phur pa kun gyi gzhi //
NG0282:8421: bstan pa dar dang 'dul ba'i don //
NG0282:8422: gang du bstan par 'byung bar byed //
NG0282:8423: rang bzhin 'dul ba'i don bstan pa //
NG0282:8424: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8425: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid 'di //
NG0282:8426: chos nyid rig pa kun gyi gzhi //
NG0282:8427: rdo rje yang dag skye ba med //
NG0282:8428: spros med don rnams rtogs byed pa //
NG0282:8429: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8430: thugs rje nam mkha'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:8431: 'dul ba'i don la cir yang ston //
NG0282:8433: thams cad ma lus 'dul ba yang *//
NG0282:8434: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8435: kun tu bzang po'i ngang nyid las //
NG0282:8436: gdug pa 'dul ba'i khro bo yang *//
NG0282:8437: hum hum phat phat sgra sgrogs pa //
NG0282:8438: yongs su 'dul ba bstan pa yang *//
NG0282:8439: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8440: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs las //
NG0282:8441: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i lha //
NG0282:8442: rngam pa'i sgra yis kun bkang nas //
NG0282:8443: nyon mongs sreg par byed pa'i me //
NG0282:8444: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8445: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa yang *//
NG0282:8447: byang chub sems kyi bde ba yang *//
NG0282:8448: bde gshegs dgongs pa'i byin rlabs te //
NG0282:8449: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8450: 'dod chags sbyong zhing byang chub thob //
NG0282:8451: chags pa rang rgyud sdug bsngal sel //
NG0282:8452: zhen pa rang rgyud grol bar byed //
NG0282:8453: 'dzin pa med cing zhen pa gcod //
NG0282:8454: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8455: mkha' la bya ltar 'phur pa dang *//
NG0282:8456: chu la mi 'bying mes mi tshig / thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang *//
NG0282:8457: mngon shes rab tu mi slu dang *//
NG0282:8458: bden pa don dang ldan pa 'di //
NG0282:8459: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8460: log pa'i chos can 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:8461: dngos grub bar chad byed pa dang *//
NG0282:8462: bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa dang *//
NG0282:8463: ngan song sdug bsngal mkha' 'gror bcas //
NG0282:8464: thugs rje'i byin rlabs 'byung bar ni //
NG0282:8465: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8467: zhi dang khro dang 'dul ba'i don //
NG0282:8468: 'dul ba'i dbang du de las byung *//
NG0282:8469: drang don nges don rnam pa gnyis //
NG0282:8471: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8472: rang rgyud dngos por 'joms pa dang *//
NG0282:8473: stong pa'i don la dgod pa dang *//
NG0282:8474: bden pa'i @#/  / dbyings las 'dul ba dang *//
NG0282:8476: zhing bcu'i don rnams mthong ba dang *//
NG0282:8477: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8478: nyi ma'i 'od bzhin gsal ba dang *//
NG0282:8479: gsal la 'gyur med brtan pa dang *//
NG0282:8480: nyes pa med par rtogs pa dang *//
NG0282:8481: bgrod du med par mthar phyin pa //
NG0282:8482: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8483: skabs dang rim par gyur pa la //
NG0282:8484: sa dang lam la de bzhin te //
NG0282:8485: rim par nus pa'i byin rlabs dang *//
NG0282:8486: 'bras bu'i rim pa de bzhin te //
NG0282:8487: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8488: bsam gtan ting 'dzin rim pa ni //
NG0282:8489: ting 'dzin rtsal gyi rim pa yis //
NG0282:8490: sa la rnam pa gnyis yod de //
NG0282:8492: mya ngan 'das pa'i sa lam yang *//
NG0282:8493: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8494: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa yang *//
NG0282:8495: gang yin rtogs las de bzhin 'byung *//
NG0282:8496: ma nges 'dzin pa de bzhin bral //
NG0282:8497: 'dzin pa med pa gzhi rtsa bral //
NG0282:8498: rgyud 'di yongs su rtogs las byung *//
NG0282:8500: bstan pa yongs kyi 'byung gnas yin //
NG0282:8501: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po yin //
NG0282:8502: thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas chen yin //
NG0282:8503: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me yin //
NG0282:8504: rtogs par byed pa'i shes rab yin //
NG0282:8505: sgom par byed pa'i bsam gtan yin //
NG0282:8506: shes par byed pa'i spyod pa yin //
NG0282:8507: thob par byed pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NG0282:8508: nges par 'grub pa'i dngos grub yin //
NG0282:8509: zhi bar byed pa'i chos nyid yin //
NG0282:8510: 'jom par byed pa'i khro bo yin //
NG0282:8511: sgrol bar byed pa'i phur pa yin //
NG0282:8512: gtub par byed pa'i mtshon cha yin //
NG0282:8513: gsal bar byed pa'i mar me yin //
NG0282:8514: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:8515: rgyud 'byung ba'i don bstan pa'i le'u ste so dgu pa'o ///
NG0282:8516: / de nas bcom ldan 'das drag po nyid sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NG0282:8517: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:8518: drag po gru gsum rim pa bzhin //
NG0282:8519: dur khrod rus pa'i phye ma la //
NG0282:8520: khrag gis sbrus te rab tu byug / rim pa bzhin du byas kyang rung *//
NG0282:8521: rdzas rnams gong du bstan pa bzhin //
NG0282:8522: tshang par bsags shing las rnams bya //
NG0282:8523: bar chad bsrung zhing byin brlab bya //
NG0282:8524: phur pa sngags kyi byin brlab bya //
NG0282:8525: brjod kyis rim pas gzhug par bya //
NG0282:8527: gtso bo sngags kyis gzir la gzhag / sngags kyi las bya ting 'dzin bsgom //
NG0282:8528: rnam gsum bskyed dang mchod pa 'bul //
NG0282:8529: las bzhi brdung ba'i sbyor sgrol bya //
NG0282:8530: bstab pa'i sngags kyis de bzhin 'bul //
NG0282:8531: snying po dril zhing las rnams bya //
NG0282:8532: tshogs mchod gong du bstan pa bzhin //
NG0282:8533: de yis rtags rnams byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8534: rab tu dril zhing drag por bstan //
NG0282:8535: gong du bstan pa de min dgos //
NG0282:8536: drag po'i las su bstan pa yin //
NG0282:8537: mtshan ma brtan po byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8539: nya dkyus su bcas pa dang *//
NG0282:8540: rang rang drag po bsgral ba'i sngags //
NG0282:8541: mtha' yis brten cing gdab par bya //
NG0282:8542: dngos por 'dzin pa sgrol ba yi //
NG0282:8543: drag po khro bo'i byin rlabs yin //
NG0282:8544: dngos po stong par sgrol ba dang *//
NG0282:8545: de yi don las mi 'da' dang *//
NG0282:8547: mtshon dang dug dang brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:8548: bstab dang gnas pa'i rim pa yang *//
NG0282:8549: 'dus pa chen po rang rang yin //
NG0282:8550: gnas gsum las nyid gang byed kyang *//
NG0282:8551: rang rang sngags kyis de bzhin bya //
NG0282:8552: tshe dang bkra shis dngos grub kyang *//
NG0282:8553: thams cad 'dus pa'i sngags tshig yin //
NG0282:8554: rdo rje phur pa chen po bshad pa'i rgyud las /
NG0282:8555: drag po bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bzhi bcu pa'o //
NG0282:8556: // de nas bcom ldan 'das sras mchog sgrub pa'i
NG0282:8557: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te //
NG0282:8558: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NG0282:8559: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba bri //
NG0282:8560: dur khrod rus pa'i phye ma gdab //
NG0282:8561: sngags kyis bsrung zhing phur pa dgod //
NG0282:8562: byin brlabs dgod pa sngags nyid yin //
NG0282:8563: de nyid bskyed dang spyan drang dang *//
NG0282:8564: mchod dang las bzhi'i brdung ba dang *//
NG0282:8565: gdab cing bskul zhing snying po bzlas //
NG0282:8566: bstod bzhin gong bzhin tshogs mchod byas //
NG0282:8567: rtags rnams rab tu byung ba dang *//
NG0282:8568: bsgrub pa drag po sngags la 'jug / bsnyen bsgrub sha mdangs phyed par bya //
NG0282:8569: brdung ba'i las ni dus dus bya //
NG0282:8570: de yis rtags nyid byung ba dang *//
